ons%20to%20better%20serve%20athletes%20and%20the%20business%20with%20more%20speed%2C%20simplicity%2C%20and%20precision.%20Some%20of%20that%20work%20is%20happening%20now%20and%20more%20will%20continue%20over%20time%20as%20we%20align%20our%20teams%2C%20capabilities%2C%20and%20footprint%20to%20the%20future%20needs%20of%20the%20company.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20is%20not%20a%20new%20direction.%20It%20is%20the%20next%20phase%20of%20the%20work%20already%20underway.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20I%20outlined%20four%20actions%20we're%20taking%20across%20Operations%20to%20help%20make%20NIKE%2C%20Inc.%20a%20more%20responsive%2C%20resilient%2C%20responsible%2C%20and%20efficient%20company%3A%20optimizing%20our%20supply%20chain%20footprint%2C%20accelerating%20technology%20deployment%2C%20investing%20in%20upskilling%20our%20teams%2C%20and%20strengthening%20our%20partner%20and%20supplier%20relationships.%20The%20changes%20we%20are%20making%20now%20build%20on%20that%20work.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3EAt%20its%20core%2C%20these%20shifts%20are%20about%20building%20a%20Global%20Operations%20organization%20that%20is%20more%20focused%2C%20more%20integrated%20with%20the%20business%2C%20and%20better%20built%20for%20the%20pace%20of%20sport.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3EIn%20the%20coming%20weeks%2C%20several%20significant%20changes%20will%20take%20effect%20across%20Global%20Operations.%20These%20actions%20will%20result%20in%20changes%20to%20some%20team%20structures%2C%20work%20locations%2C%20and%20headcount.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3ETechnology%20Modernization.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cem%3EWe're%20reshaping%20our%20Technology%20team%20to%20sharpen%20alignment%20with%20the%20business%2C%20build%20leaner%20teams%2C%20and%20accelerate%20what%20matters%20most.%20This%20means%20consolidating%20our%20technology%20footprint%2C%20streamlining%20our%20structure%20to%20move%20with%20greater%20speed%20and%20focus%2C%20and%20doubling%20down%20on%20the%20locations%20where%20our%20work%20gets%20done%20with%20a%20focus%20on%20two%20strategically%20important%20hubs%20%E2%80%94%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EPhilip%20H.%20Knight%20Campus%20and%20our%20Nike%20India%20Technology%20Center%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cem%3E.%20These%20are%20deliberate%20moves%20to%20build%20a%20leaner%2C%20faster%2C%20more%20connected%20Technology%20organization%20%E2%80%94%20one%20built%20to%20deliver%20for%20the%20consumer%2C%20the%20athlete%2C%20and%20the%20business.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EAir%20Manufacturing%20Modernization.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%20We%20are%20modernizing%20how%20work%20gets%20done%20across%20our%20Air%20Manufacturing%20Innovation%20(Air%20MI)%20facilities%20in%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EBeaverton%2C%20Ore.%3B%20St.%20Louis%3B%20and%20Vietnam%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%20by%20increasing%20resiliency%2C%20streamlining%20processes%2C%20and%20adjusting%20staffing%20to%20match%20the%20needs%20of%20the%20business.%20The%20changes%20will%20help%20us%20stay%20flexible%20as%20demand%20changes%2C%20accelerate%20future%20innovations%20and%20continue%20to%20deliver%20the%20product%20quality%20athletes%20expect%20from%20Nike.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EConverse%20Ground%20Game.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cem%3EWe%20are%20moving%20some%20Converse%20Footwear%20Manufacturing%20and%20Engineering%20resources%20closer%20to%20our%20factory%20partners%20to%20enable%20stronger%20real-time%20collaboration%20and%20to%20better%20support%20the%20brand's%20needs%20going%20forward.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EMaterials%20Supply%20Chain%20Integration.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cem%3EWe%20are%20bringing%20our%20Materials%20Supply%20Chain%20work%20more%20directly%20into%20our%20Footwear%20and%20Apparel%20Supply%20Chain%20teams%20while%20continuing%20to%20build%20on%20the%20valuable%20capabilities%20already%20in%20place.%20This%20strengthens%20how%20we%20operate%20from%20raw%20materials%20through%20finished%20product%2C%20enabling%20faster%20more%20synchronized%20decisions%20and%20ground-breaking%20innovations%20across%20our%20best-in-class%20manufacturing%20network.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3ECollectively%2C%20these%20changes%20will%20result%20in%20a%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3Ereduction%20of%20approximately%201%2C400%20roles%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cem%3Ein%20Global%20Operations%2C%20with%20the%20majority%20in%20Technology.%20These%20reductions%20are%20very%20hard%20for%20the%20teammates%20directly%20affected%20and%20for%20the%20teams%20around%20them%2C%20too.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3EPart%20of%20doing%20the%20right%20thing%20is%20being%20direct.%20Another%20part%20is%20making%20sure%20people%20are%20treated%20with%20care.%20Teammates%20whose%20roles%20are%20impacted%20will%20hear%20directly%20from%20their%20leaders%20and%20HR%20partners%20starting%20today%2C%20and%20we%20will%20work%20to%20make%20sure%20they%20have%20clear%20information%20and%20support%20through%20this%20transition.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3ETo%20teammates%20whose%20roles%20are%20impacted%2C%20thank%20you.%20Your%20contributions%20have%20helped%20build%20this%20company%2C%20and%20we%20are%20grateful%20for%20the%20work%2C%20commitment%2C%20and%20care%20you%20have%20brought%20to%20Nike.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3ETo%20the%20broader%20team%2C%20moments%20like%20this%20require%20professionalism%2C%20empathy%2C%20and%20a%20shared%20commitment%20to%20one%20another.%20These%20changes%20are%20meant%20to%20make%20the%20company%20less%20complex%20and%20more%20responsive.%20As%20we%20look%20ahead%2C%20that%20means%20simplifying%20parts%20of%20how%20we%20operate%2C%20using%20more%20advanced%20automation%20where%20it%20helps%20us%20work%20better%2C%20and%20building%20an%20even%20stronger%20end-to-end%20foundation%20for%20future%20growth.%20I%20expect%20these%20efforts%20to%20continue%20beyond%20our%20Win%20Now%20action%20plan.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Operations%20team%20has%20played%2C%20is%20playing%2C%20and%20will%20play%20an%20important%20role%20in%20helping%20NIKE%2C%20Inc.%20strengthen%20its%20foundation%20and%20it%20will%20continue%20to%20play%20a%20critical%20role%20in%20the%20company's%20comeback.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3EThank%20you%20for%20your%20leadership%2C%20your%20dedication%20to%20the%20athletes%2C%20and%20your%20dedication%20to%20each%20other.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3EVenkatesh%20Alagirisamy%3Cbr%3EEVP%2C%20Chief%20Operating%20Officer%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fread-memo-nike-reduces-workforce-1-400-roles-tech-shifts-2026-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1776985297000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69ea9810a98bc8fdc096e343%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fread-memo-nike-reduces-workforce-1-400-roles-tech-shifts-2026-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nike%20announced%201%2C400%20job%20cuts%20in%20global%20operations%20on%20Thursday%2C%20as%20it%20focuses%20on%20modernizing%20tech%20and%20manufacturing%20as%20part%20of%20its%20turnaround%20plan.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jhart%40insider.com%20(Jordan%20Hart)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Apex%E2%80%99%20Review%3A%20Man%20Is%20the%20Predator%20in%20a%20Rip-Roaring%20Outdoor%20Duel%20Between%20Charlize%20Theron%20and%20Taron%20Egerton%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1776985200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2