he%20used%20classified%20military%20information%20to%20make%20bets%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpolymarket-informed-insider-trades-study-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eprediction%20market%20platform%20Polymarket%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20winning%20more%20than%20%24400%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGannon%20Ken%20Van%20Dyke%2C%20a%20Special%20Forces%20master%20sergeant%20who%20worked%20out%20of%20Fort%20Bragg%20in%20North%20Carolina%2C%20was%20charged%20with%20felonies%2C%20including%20wire%20fraud%20and%20violating%20the%20Commodity%20Exchange%20Act%2C%20federal%20prosecutors%20in%20Manhattan%20announced.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVan%20Dyke%2C%20prosecutors%20said%20in%20a%20statement%2C%20%26quot%3Bwas%20involved%20in%20the%20planning%20and%20execution%20of%20Operation%20Absolute%20Resolve%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20military%20operation%20to%20capture%20Venezuela's%20Nicolas%20Maduro%2C%20%26quot%3Band%20had%20access%20to%20sensitive%2C%20nonpublic%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flawmakers-staff-ban-prediction-markets-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eclassified%20information%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20that%20operation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProsecutors%20say%20he%20used%20that%20information%20to%20place%2013%20bets%20between%20December%2027%2C%202025%2C%20and%20January%202%2C%202026%20%E2%80%94%20wagering%20more%20than%20%2433%2C000%20%E2%80%94%20in%20which%20he%20had%20an%20affirmative%20position%20on%20the%20question%20of%20whether%20the%20US%20would%20take%20action%20in%20Venezuela%20or%20against%20Maduro.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20is%20accused%20of%20withdrawing%20his%20winnings%20%E2%80%94%20a%20profit%20of%20%24409%2C881%20%E2%80%94%20the%20day%20of%20the%20US%20raid%20on%20Venezuela%20and%20depositing%20it%20first%20in%20a%20foreign%20cryptocurrency%20vault%20and%20then%20an%20online%20brokerage%20account.%20The%20feds%20say%20he%20also%20took%20steps%20to%20conceal%20his%20identity%20after%20speculation%20about%20the%20large%2C%20curiously%20timed%20trades%20began%20circulating%2C%20and%20asked%20Polymarket%20to%20delete%20his%20account%20using%20a%20phone%20excuse.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENo%20attorney%20for%20Van%20Dyke%2C%2037%2C%20who%20has%20been%20an%20active-duty%20soldier%20since%202008%2C%20was%20listed%20in%20the%20court%20docket.%20A%20family%20member%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20Polymarket%20said%20it%20tipped%20off%20the%20feds%20to%20Van%20Dyke's%20trades.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLast%20month%2C%20we%20published%20our%20enhanced%20market%20integrity%20rules%20to%20combat%20insider%20trading.%20When%20we%20identified%20a%20user%20trading%20on%20classified%20government%20information%2C%20we%20referred%20the%20matter%20to%20the%20DOJ%20%26amp%3B%20cooperated%20with%20their%20investigation%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20company%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BInsider%20trading%20has%20no%20place%20on%20Polymarket.%20Today's%20arrest%20is%20proof%20the%20system%20works.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInsider%20trading%20is%20a%20major%20issue%20for%20prediction%20markets%2C%20which%20allow%20people%20to%20buy%20and%20sell%20contracts%20%E2%80%94in%20other%20words%2C%20trade%20%E2%80%94%20on%20the%20outcome%20of%20real-world%20events.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20Polymarket%20rival%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkalshi-suspends-political-candidates-trading-elections-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EKalshi%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%20it%20had%20suspended%20and%20fined%20three%20candidates%20for%20political%20office%20for%20making%20trades%20related%20to%20their%20own%20elections.%20In%20February%2C%20Kalshi%20banned%20and%20fined%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkalshi-bans-fines-users-youtube-streamer-california-politician-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EMrBeast%20editor%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20it%20said%20had%20traded%20on%20markets%20related%20to%20YouTube%20streaming.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVan%20Dyke%20faces%20a%20far%20harsher%20penalty%20if%20convicted%3A%20The%20most%20serious%20charge%20against%20him%2C%20wire%20fraud%2C%20carries%20up%20to%2020%20years%20in%20prison.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Commodity%20Futures%20Trading%20Commission%2C%20which%20regulates%20prediction%20markets%2C%20filed%20a%20civil%20complaint%20against%20Van%20Dyke%20in%20federal%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20been%20crystal%20clear%20that%20anyone%20who%20engages%20in%20fraud%2C%20manipulation%2C%20or%20insider%20trading%20in%20any%20of%20our%20markets%20will%20face%20the%20full%20force%20of%20the%20law%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwho-is-michael-selig-prediction-markets-cftc-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EChairman%20Michael%20S.%20Selig%20%3C%2Fa%3Esaid%20in%20a%20statement.%20%26quot%3BThe%20defendant%20was%20entrusted%20with%20confidential%20information%20about%20US%20operations%20and%20yet%20took%20action%20that%20endangered%20US%20national%20security%20and%20put%20the%20lives%20of%20American%20service%20members%20in%20harm's%20way.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESelig%20has%20defended%20prediction%20markets%2C%20saying%20in%20February%2C%20%26quot%3BIt's%20something%20that%20I%20think%20is%20valuable%20to%20society.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Farmy-soldier-gannon-van-dyke-indicted-military-secrets-polymarket-2026-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1776983397000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69ea98dba98bc8fdc096e34b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Farmy-soldier-gannon-van-dyke-indicted-military-secrets-polymarket-2026-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Gannon%20Ken%20Van%20Dyke%20was%20indicted%20on%20charges%20of%20using%20classified%20i