20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fclaude%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EClaude%20Code%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20sucked%20lately%2C%20Anthropic%20just%20confirmed%20it%20wasn't%20all%20in%20your%20head.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20wrote%20in%20a%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.anthropic.com%2Fengineering%2Fapril-23-postmortem%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elengthy%20blog%20post%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0that%20after%20reviewing%20user%20complaints%20about%20the%20quality%20of%20Claude%20Code%2C%20one%20of%20its%20most%20popular%20products%2C%20it%20identified%20three%20issues%20likely%20contributing%20to%20a%20worse%20user%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20take%20reports%20about%20degradation%20very%20seriously.%20We%20never%20intentionally%20degrade%20our%20models%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Thursday%20post%20read.%20It%20said%20the%20underlying%20model%20was%20not%20affected%3B%20the%20issues%20were%20tweaks%20made%20at%20the%20product%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20April%2020%2C%20Anthropic%20said%2C%20those%20issues%20were%20fixed%20and%20that%20it%20had%20taken%20steps%20to%20avoid%20similar%20problems%20in%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20post%20came%20after%20weeks%20of%20user%20complaints%20that%20Claude%20Code's%20responses%20had%20deteriorated.%20The%20complaints%20followed%20a%20series%20of%20wins%20for%20Anthropic%2C%20which%20has%20been%20praised%20for%20the%20technical%20abilities%20of%20its%20tools%20and%20earned%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-trillion-dollar-valuation-on-secondary-markets-2026%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%241%20trillion%20valuation%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20secondary%20markets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20issues%20led%20some%20users%20to%20speculate%20that%20Anthropic%20had%20intentionally%20degraded%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-claude-opus-4-7-backlash-tokens-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Bnerfed%26quot%3B%20the%20tool%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20the%20company%20flatly%20denied.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BClaude%20has%20regressed%20to%20the%20point%20it%20cannot%20be%20trusted%20to%20perform%20complex%20engineering%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20GitHub%20user%20identified%20as%20Stella%20Laurenzo%2C%20senior%20director%20of%20chipmaker%20AMD's%20AI%20group%2C%20wrote%20in%20a%20post%20from%20early%20April.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESimilar%20complaints%20were%20shared%20on%20Reddit%2C%20where%20one%20user%20said%20Claude%20Code%20had%20become%20%26quot%3Blazy%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3Bignorant%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bdegraded%20and%20myopic.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOver%20the%20past%20month%2C%20some%20of%20you%20reported%20Claude%20Code's%20quality%20had%20slipped%2C%26quot%3B%20Anthropic's%20developers%20said%20in%20an%20X%20post%20on%20Thursday.%20%26quot%3BWe%20investigated%2C%20and%20published%20a%20post-mortem%20on%20the%20three%20issues%20we%20found.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20detailed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-compute-limits-anthropic-github-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eproduct%20changes%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20led%20to%20the%20reported%20problems%3A%20a%20change%20to%20Claude%20Code's%20default%20thinking%20level%2C%20a%20cache-optimization%20tweak%20that%20introduced%20a%20bug%2C%20and%20a%20system%20prompt%20meant%20to%20make%20the%20tool%20less%20verbose.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESteps%20taken%20to%20solve%20the%20problem%20include%20having%20a%20larger%20share%20of%20staff%20use%20the%20public%20build%20of%20Claude%20Code%2C%20improving%20its%20code%20review%20tool%2C%20and%20adding%20tighter%20controls%20to%20system%20prompt%20changes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20thanked%20users%20who%20submitted%20feedback%20and%20said%20it%20is%20resetting%20usage%20limits%20for%20all%20subscribers%20as%20of%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20Claude%20users%20expressed%20feeling%20validated%20after%20Anthropic's%20announcement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20can't%20believe%20we%20were%20right%2C%26quot%3B%20popular%20X%20user%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Flevelsio%2Fstatus%2F2047387029915271445%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%40levelsio%3C%2Fa%3E%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BClaude%20was%20dumbified%20on%20March%204%2C%20just%20when%20we%20noticed!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20user%20reshared%20their%20March%204%20post%20%E2%80%94%20the%20day%20Anthropic%20said%20it%20had%20changed%20the%20default%20thinking%20level%20%E2%80%94%20that%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BClaude%20Code%20with%20Opus%204.6%20was%20so%20dumb%20today%20I%20finally%20had%20to%20write%20my%20own%20code%20again.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnthropic%20also%20received%20some%20scrutiny%20on%20Tuesday%20when%20it%20said%20it%20was%20experimenting%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-claude-code-price-confusion-sam-altman-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eremoving%20Claude%20Code%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20Pro%20plan%2C%20its%20lower-tier%20paid%20subscription.%20The%20company%20said%20it%20was%20a%20test%20that%20affected%20around%202%25%20of%20new%20users.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-admits-claude-code-issues-user-complaints-denies-nerfing-degrading-2026-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1776981780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69ea8bae367066d7c2970609%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-admits-claude-code-issues-user-complaints-denies-nerfing-degrading-2026-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Anthropic%20said%20it%20found%20three%20issues%20with%20Claude%20Code%20after%20users%20complained%20the%20AI%20tool%20deteriorated.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22kvlamis%40businessinsider.com%20(Kelsey%20Vlamis)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonic