0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Famazon-music-unlimited-deal%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esign%20up%20for%20four%20months%20of%20Amazon%20Music%20Unlimited%3C%2Fa%3E%20(a%20service%20that%20usually%20costs%20%247.99%20a%20month%20for%20Prime%20members)%20for%20just%20%241.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EI%20love%20listening%20to%20music%2C%20so%20I%20was%20surprised%20that%20it%20took%20me%20so%20long%20to%20discover%20Amazon%20Prime's%20music%20offerings.%20I%20had%20%3Cem%3Eheard%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Ethat%20Amazon%20had%20a%20music%20selection%2C%20but%20I%20really%20never%20took%20the%20time%20to%20check%20it%20out%20until%20a%20few%20weeks%20ago.%20If%20you%20have%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Famazon-prime-benefits%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmazon%20Prime%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20you%20may%20already%20know%20about%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Famzn.to%2F2Rz1MIV%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPrime%20Music%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20a%20limited%20but%20free%20streaming%20service%20that%20comes%20with%20your%20membership.%20Then%20there's%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Famzn.to%2F2X4OWIh%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmazon%20Music%20Unlimited%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20premium%20streaming%20service%20that%20Prime%20members%20can%20get%20at%20a%20discounted%20rate%20of%20%247.99%20a%20month%20(%249.99%20if%20you%20don't%20have%20Prime).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPrime%20Music%20and%20Music%20Unlimited%20share%20many%20features%2C%20so%20it%20can%20be%20a%20little%20confusing%20to%20understand%20what%20each%20really%20offers.%20To%20make%20it%20easy%20for%20you%2C%20we're%20going%20to%20give%20you%20a%20quick%20breakdown%20of%20their%20similarities%20and%20differences.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22556134bf-d145-47eb-9469-9c7d4941be1a%5C%22%3EAmazon%20Music%20Unlimited%20vs.%20Prime%20Music%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22prime%20music%20compare%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5d12735fe3ecba0b1b7cf4c5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMusic%20Unlimited%20v.%20Prime%20Music%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%2F%20Remi%20Rosmarin%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223ea4b06d-f3fa-49e9-bfcb-520b472d4004%5C%22%3ESimilarities%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon%20Music%20Unlimited%20is%20the%20souped-up%20version%20of%20Prime%20Music.%20But%2C%20at%20the%20core%20of%20it%2C%20both%20of%20the%20services%20share%20a%20variety%20of%20features.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EAd-free%20listening%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Whether%20you%20have%20the%20free%20version%20or%20pay%20for%20the%20premium%20upgrade%2C%20Amazon%20will%20always%20let%20you%20listen%20without%20ads.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EOn%20demand%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Many%20%26quot%3Bfreemium%26quot%3B%20streaming%20services%20don't%20let%20you%20listen%20on%20demand%20unless%20you%20pay%20for%20the%20service.%20That%20means%20you%20have%20to%20listen%20in%20shuffle%20mode%20and%20can%20only%20skip%20a%20number%20of%20songs%20a%20day.%20With%20both%20Amazon%20services%2C%20you%20can%20skip%20an%20unlimited%20number%20of%20songs%20and%20listen%20for%20as%20many%20hours%20as%20you'd%20like.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EInterface%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20The%20interface%20is%20the%20same%20across%20both%20services.%20You'll%20find%20thousands%20of%20curated%20playlists%20and%20personalized%20stations%20based%20on%20your%20listening%20history%20in%20both%20models.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlexa%20interaction%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20You%20can%20use%20your%20voice%20to%20control%20music%20playback%20through%20Alexa%20with%20both%20services.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EOffline%20listening%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Both%20services%20let%20you%20stream%20music%20when%20you're%20offline%2C%20except%20for%20the%20Music%20Unlimited%20single-device%20plan%2C%20which%20is%20the%20lowest-cost%20option%20that%20works%20solely%20with%20one%20Alexa-enabled%20device%20%E2%80%94%20this%20is%20understandable%20as%20you%20need%20internet%20to%20power%20your%20Alexa%20device.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cad35105-0de7-48b7-9b72-b5f57a2e4038%5C%22%3EDifferences%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ESelection%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20The%20most%20notable%20difference%2C%20in%20my%20opinion%2C%20is%20the%20selection.%20Prime%20Music's%20%3Cstrong%3E2%20million%20songs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20may%20sound%20like%20a%20lot%2C%20but%20most%20streaming%20services%20offer%20tens%20of%20millions%20of%20songs%20%E2%80%94%20making%202%20million%20look%20pretty%20meager.%20Prime%20Music%20has%20a%20variety%20of%20artists%2C%20but%20many%20of%20my%20favorite%20artists%20only%20had%20one%20song%20on%20the%20platform.%20With%20%3Cstrong%3E50%20million%20songs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20Music%20Unlimited%20fills%20all%20the%20holes.%20I%20was%20impressed%20by%20the%20selection%20and%20did%20not%20feel%20that%20it%20was%20lacking%20in%20any%20way.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EPrice%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Prime%20Music%20is%20%3Cstrong%3Efree%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20if%20you%20have%20Amazon%20Prime.%20If%20you're%20not%2C%20this%20unfortunately%20isn't%20a%20service%20you%20can%20opt%20into%20%E2%80%94%20rather%2C%20it's%20a%20nice%20free%20perk%20for%20Prime%20members.%20Music%20Unlimited%20is%20%3Cstrong%3E%247.99%20a%20month%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20for%20Prime%20Members%2C%20or%20%3Cstrong%3E%2479%20a%20year%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20a%20pretty%20affordable%20price%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20streaming%20services.%20If%20you%20don't%20have%20a%20Prime%20membership%2C%20Music%20Unlimited%20will%20cost%20you%20%3Cstrong%3E%249.99%20a%20month%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20which%20is%20around%20the%20industry%20standard.%20Music%20Unlimited%20also%20offers%20student%20discounts%20and%20family%20plans.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EVoice%20commands%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20If%20you%20love%20your%20Alexa%20device%2C%20Music%20Unlimited%20offers%20even%20more%20voice%20commands.%20You%20can%20ask%20Alexa%20to%20play%20a%20specific%20song%20or%20just%20give%20a%20vague%20request%20like%20%26quot%3BAlexa%2C%20play%20upbeat%20country%20music%26quot%3B%20and%20see%20what%20she%20picks.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EExclusive%20content%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Music%20Unlimited%20lets%20you%20pull%20back%20the%20curtains%20and%20go%20behind%20the%20scenes%20of%20some%20of%20your%20favorite%20songs.%20Side-by-sides%2C%20as%20they're%20called%2C%20offer%20exclusive%20artist%20commentary%20on%20their%20own%20songs%20and%20albums.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a84d48b0-9092-4680-a92e-aa96c7ab7cd2%5C%22%3EBottom%20line%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20have%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Famzn.to%2F2IJncjC%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmazon%20Prime%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20congrats%20%E2%80%94%20you%20already%20have%20Prime%20Music.%20This%20is%20definitely%20a%20nice%20added%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Famazon-prime-benefits%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eperk%20to%20the%20Prime%20membership%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20especially%20since%20it's%20at%20no%20extra%20cost%20to%20you.%C2%A0If%20you%20like%20listening%20to%20music%20in%20discovery%20mode%2C%20and%20aren't%20too%20particular%20about%20what%20you're%20listening%20too%2C%20then%20Prime%20Music%20may%20be%20enough%20for%20you.%20But%2C%20if%20you%20like%20to%20listen%20to%20the%20songs%20you%20want%2C%20when%20you%20want%20them%2C%20you%20may%20feel%20let%20down%20by%20Prime%20Music's%20small%20selection.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Famzn.to%2F2X4OWIh%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmazon%20Music%20Unlimited%3C%2Fa%3E%20comes%20at%20an%20added%20cost%2C%20but%20it%20may%20be%20worth%20it%20for%20some%20listeners.%20If%20you're%20someone%20who%20loves%20to%20use%20your%20Alexa%20devices%2C%20and%20are%20particularly%20involved%20in%20the%20Amazon%20sphere%2C%20a%20service%20like%20Music%20Unlimited%20will%20probably%20serve%20you%20well%20%E2%80%94%20it%20has%20a%20large%20catalog%20of%20songs%2C%20integrates%20well%20with%20Alexa%2C%20and%20account%20management%20and%20payments%20are%20simplified%20with%20your%20existing%20Amazon%20login.%20If%20you%20already%20have%20Amazon%20Prime%2C%20this%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20affordable%20streaming%20services%20around.%20If%20you%20don't%2C%20you%20can%20try%20the%20service%20for%20free%20for%2030%20days.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20don't%20have%20Amazon%20Prime%20already%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Famzn.to%2F2IJncjC%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esign%20up%20for%20a%20free%20trial%20now%3C%2Fa%3E%20so%20you%20can%20experience%20Prime%20Music.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22909eaee4-f43e-4e9b-909c-ae4d78a44fe4%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Famzn.to%2F2Rz1MIV%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIf%20you%20have%20Amazon%20Prime%2C%20listen%20to%20Prime%20Music%20for%20free%20now%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b2a1ac11-9f6e-412d-9b4d-64968b83a6a6%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Famzn.to%2F2X4OWIh%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETry%20Amazon%20Music%20Unlimited%20free%20for%2030%20days%20(then%20pay%20%249.99%20a%20month%2C%20or%20%247.99%20a%20month%20with%20Prime)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fprime-music-vs-amazon-music-unlimited%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1776979020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%