municates%20with%20all%20of%20the%20sensors%2C%20your%20smartphone%2C%20and%20the%20professional%20monitoring.%20SimpliSafe%20recommends%20installing%20this%20in%20a%20central%20spot%20in%20your%20home.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EKeypad%20%E2%80%94%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20keypad%20is%20installed%20next%20to%20your%20main%20entrance%20so%20you%20can%20easily%20enter%20your%20PIN%20to%20turn%20it%20off%20when%20you%20get%20home.%20It%20also%20tells%20you%20if%20the%20alarm%20has%20been%20triggered%20and%20if%20there%20are%20any%20software%20updates.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EEntry%20sensors%20(3)%20%E2%80%94%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20These%20two-piece%20units%20go%20on%20doors%20and%20windows.%20They%20let%20you%20know%20when%20a%20potential%20point%20of%20entry%20is%20opened%20or%20closed.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EMotion%20sensor%20%E2%80%94%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20This%20uses%20infrared%20technology%20to%20tell%20if%20someone%20enters%20a%20room.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EGlassbreak%20sensor%20%E2%80%94%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Installed%20on%20a%20wall%20or%20shelf%20within%2030%20feet%20of%20windows%20that%20are%20most%20likely%20to%20be%20broken%20into%2C%20the%20glassbreak%20sensor%20is%20triggered%20when%20it%20%26quot%3Bhears%26quot%3B%20the%20specific%20frequency%20of%20glass%20breaking.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EPanic%20button%20%E2%80%94%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20I%20put%20this%20by%20my%20bed%20%E2%80%94%20you%20just%20push%20it%20if%20there%20is%20a%20threat%20that%20the%20other%20sensors%20didn't%20pick%20up.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EFreeze%20sensor%20%E2%80%94%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20This%20sensor%20monitors%20the%20temperature%20in%20your%20house%20and%20sends%20an%20alert%20if%20it%20gets%20too%20cold%20or%20too%20hot.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EWater%20sensor%20%E2%80%94%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20If%20your%20basement%20is%20flooding%2C%20you%20want%20to%20know%20right%20away.%20The%20water%20sensor%20will%20alert%20you.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInstallation%20of%20these%20units%20took%20a%20total%20of%2045%20minutes.%20This%20included%20reading%20the%20manual%2C%20installing%20the%20app%2C%20installing%20the%20sensors%2C%20and%20testing.%20There%20were%20no%20tools%20needed.%20All%20of%20the%20devices%20have%20adhesives%20on%20them%20that%20make%20it%20easy%20to%20stick%20them%20to%20the%20walls.%20They%20also%20come%20with%20screws%20if%20you%20want%20to%20mount%20them%20that%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3ERead%20more%3A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-security-camera-home%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20best%20security%20cameras%20you%20can%20buy%20for%20your%20home%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15126323980h7-20%26h%3D7480bbbfa39fb3c6a632c59997bac02d423c823d780a4aba1f21a3fc711e786e%26postID%3D61b8efc7f2a36b1ac9f42942%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Ftech%252Fsimplisafe-home-security-system-review%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fwww.anrdoezrs.net%252Flinks%252F6415797%252Ftype%252Fdlg%252Fsid%252Fbiip_102618_simplisafe-review%252Fhttps%253A%252F%252Fsimplisafe.com%252Fhome-security-system-essentials%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESimpliSafe%3C%2Fa%3E%20performed%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20SimpliSafe%2C%20you%20can%20self-monitor%20or%20pay%20%2414.99%20per%20month%20(no%20contract%20required)%20for%2024%2F7%20professional%20monitoring.%20If%20you%20choose%20to%20self-monitor%2C%20the%20onus%20is%20on%20you%20to%20assess%20the%20threat%20and%20contact%20the%20police%20when%20you%20receive%20an%20alert.%20Self-monitoring%20fails%20when%20you%20are%20in%20a%20compromised%20position%20and%20cannot%20contact%20the%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20SimpliSafe's%20professional%20monitoring%20and%20police%20dispatch%2C%20they%20call%20you%20when%20the%20alarm%20is%20triggered.%20If%20you%20don't%20answer%2C%20they%20contact%20the%20backup%20number.%20If%20the%20secondary%20contact%20doesn't%20answer%2C%20then%20a%20SimpliSafe%20representative%20calls%20911.%20Because%20of%20false%20alarms%20tying%20up%20police%20resources%2C%20different%20municipalities%20have%20different%20processes%20for%20these%20calls.%20For%20instance%2C%20in%20order%20for%20a%20third-party%20to%20contact%20police%20on%20your%20behalf%2C%20some%20cities%20require%20you%20to%20register%20your%20security%20system%20and%20also%20provide%20some%20sort%20of%20audio%20or%20video%20proof%20of%20a%20crime%20in%20progress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20set%20off%20the%20alarm%20a%20couple%20of%20times.%20Within%20about%2010%20minutes%20of%20leaving%20the%20house%20after%20first%20arming%20the%20system%2C%20I%20got%20a%20call%20from%20SimpliSafe%20asking%20if%20I%20had%20an%20emergency%20event%20because%20the%20motion%20sensor%20had%20been%20triggered%20by%20my%20dog.%20I%20gave%20the%20representative%20my%20safe%20word%2C%20and%20there%20was%20no%20need%20for%20a%20police%20dispatch.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20setup%20guide%20directs%20you%20on%20how%20to%20place%20the%20motion%20sensor%20if%20you%20have%20cats%20or%20dogs%20but%20not%20both.%20I%20have%20two%20cats%20and%20a%20dog.%20I%20emailed%20SimpliSafe's%20customer%20service%20on%20a%20Sunday%20evening%20for%20help%20on%20the%20correct%20placement%20of%20the%20motion%20sensor%2C%20and%20they%20got%20back%20to%20me%20the%20next%20morning.%20The%20service%20rep%20recommended%20installing%20the%20motion%20sensor%20upside%20down%20about%20four%20feet%20above%20the%20floor.%20This%20is%20because%20the%20sensor%20doesn't%20monitor%20upwards.%20So%2C%20people%20four%20feet%20tall%20and%20taller%20will%20set%20it%20off.%20Four-legged%20creatures%20will%20not.%20Once%20I%20resolved%20this%2C%20I%20didn't%20have%20any%20other%20false%20alarms%20from%20the%20motion%20sensor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20app%20is%20incredibly%20easy%20to%20use%20and%20makes%20it%20effortless%20to%20customize%20your%20experience.%20You%20can%20choose%20to%20get%20push%20notifications%2C%20SMS%20texts%2C%20or%20emails%20when%20any%20of%20your%20sensors%20are%20triggered.%20There%20is%20also%20an%20option%20to%20instantly%20sound%20the%20alarm.%20I%20set%20this%20up%20for%20when%20the%20glassbreak%20sensor%20is%20triggered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3ERead%20more%3A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-diy-home-security-products%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20best%20home%20security%20products%20you%20can%20buy%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ESome%20concerns%20about%20the%20home%20security%20system%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%2095%20decibels%2C%20the%20alarm%20is%20quite%20loud%2C%20but%20it%20may%20not%20reach%20all%20parts%20of%20your%20home.%20SimpliSafe%20instructs%20you%20to%20install%20the%20base%20station%20in%20a%20central%20location%20in%20your%20home.%20At%20first%2C%20we%20figured%20that%20would%20be%20the%20second%20floor%20of%20our%20three-story%20home.%20But%2C%20from%20the%20first%20floor%2C%20where%20intruders%20will%20likely%20enter%2C%20the%20sound%20of%20the%20siren%20was%20not%20as%20intense%20as%20we%20would%20have%20liked.%20So%2C%20we%20moved%20the%20siren%20to%20the%20first%20floor.%20It%20would%20be%20nice%20if%20SimpliSafe%20offered%20a%20few%20sirens%20throughout%20the%20home.%20For%20%2460%2C%20SimpliSafe%20offer%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15126323980h7-20%26h%3D860d6e852353869140c2229697a1767807dfcc0310981d25b16b330934c2fd31%26postID%3D61b8efc7f2a36b1ac9f42942%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Ftech%252Fsimplisafe-home-security-system-review%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fwww.anrdoezrs.net%252Flinks%252F6415797%252Ftype%252Fdlg%252Fsid%252Fbiip_102618_simplisafe-review%252Fhttps%253A%252F%252Fsimplisafe.com%252Fbuild-my-system%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ean%20extra-loud%20105-decibel%20siren%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0that%20can%20be%20used%20inside%20the%20home%20or%20outside%20to%20alert%20neighbors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20wanted%20to%20keep%20the%20key%20fob%20on%20my%20keychain%20for%20easy%20access%2C%20but%20I%20accidentally%20armed%20the%20system%20while%20it%20was%20in%20my%20pocket.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20I%20was%20next%20door%20talking%20to%20my%20neighbor%20and%20didn't%20have%20my%20phone%20on%20me.%20I%20faintly%20heard%20an%20alarm-like%20sound%2C%20but%20I%20assumed%20it%20was%20coming%20from%20elsewhere.%20Well%2C%20it%20turns%20out%20it%20was%20our%20system%20and%20my%20wife%20got%20a%20call%20from%20the%20SimpliSafe%20rep.%20Now%2C%20I%20just%20keep%20the%20key%20fob%20next%20to%20my%20bed%20to%20arm%20the%20system%20when%20I%20go%20to%20bed.%20I%20use%20the%20keypad%20when%20leaving%20the%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELastly%2C%20there's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsimplisafe-security-system-hack-2016-2%5C%22%3Ea%20reported%20hack%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20can%20disarm%20the%20second-generation%20SimpliSafe%20system.%20The%20signals%20for%20the%20new%20third-gen%20system%20are%20encrypted%20and%20should%20protect%20against%20this%20hack.%20If%20you%20are%20concerned%20about%20this%2C%20I%20recommend%20not%20advertising%20that%20you%20are%20using%20a%20SimpliSafe%20system.%20Instead%2C%20consider%20purchasing%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Famzn.to%2F2EVwjOa%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egeneric%20signs%3C%2Fa%3E%20off%20Amazon%20or%20elsewhere.%20Either%20way%2C%20it's%20important%20that%20you%20advertise%20that%20you%20have%20a%20security%20system.%20That%20should%20be%20enough%20to%20deter%20most%20scofflaws.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20bottom%20line%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20the%20best%20security%20system%20won't%20stop%20a%20determined%20burglar.%20But%2C%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20opportunistic%20crimes%2C%20a%20security%20system%20should%20be%20enough%20to%20ward%20off%20most%20criminals.%20In%20the%20five%20months%20we've%20lived%20here%2C%20we%20haven't%20had%20any%20security%20issues.%20And%2C%20my%20wife%20and%20I%20sleep%20easier%20at%20night%20knowing%20that%20our%20home%20is%20being%20monitored%2024%2F7.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBased%20on%20my%20experience%2C%20the%20third-generation%20of%20SimpliSafe's%20wireless%20home%20security%20system%20is%20everything%20it%20claims%20to%20be.%20I%20strongly%20recommend%20it%20for%20safeguarding%20your%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15126323980h7-20%26h%3D7480bbbfa39fb3c6a632c59997bac02d423c823d780a4aba1f21a3fc711e786e%26postID%3D61b8efc7f2a36b1ac9f42942%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Ftech%252Fsimplisafe-home-security-system-review%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fwww.anrdoezrs.net%252Flinks%252F6415797%252Ftype%252Fdlg%252Fsid%252Fbiip_102618_simplisafe-review%252Fhttps%253A%252F%252Fsimplisafe.com%252Fhome-security-system-essentials%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBuy%20The%20Essentials%206-piece%20SimpliSafe%20Wireless%20Home%20Security%20System%20for%20%24221%20on%20SimpliSafe%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Famzn.to%2F2yBnMdH%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBuy%20the%20SimpliSafe%20Wireless%20Home%20Security%20System%20starting%20at%20%24249.99%20on%20Amazon%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3EUpdate%2010%2F30%2F18%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20After%20this%20review%20was%20published%2C%20SimpliSafe%20contacted%20us%20to%20let%20us%20know%20about%20their%20video%20alarm%20verification.%20If%20you%20have