duct%25253Ficmp%25253DLP-SHCC-MP-NO-educat-142%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESpike%20Prime%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20STEAM-based%20education%20tool%20from%20Lego%20that%20involves%20a%20kit%20of%20528%20Lego%20and%20Technic%20bricks%20%E2%80%94%20most%20will%20be%20familiar%20to%20Lego%20fans%2C%20while%20others%20are%20custom%20to%20Spike%20Prime%2C%20including%20sensors%2C%20motors%2C%20and%20wires.%20At%20the%20heart%20of%20everything%20is%20the%20Hub%2C%20a%20programmable%20control%20box%20that%20the%20user%20attaches%20all%20the%20bricks%20and%20wires%20onto.%20With%20the%20hub%2C%20you%20can%20create%20a%20break-dancing%20robot%2C%20a%20weather%20station%2C%20a%20hopping%20frog%2C%20or%20any%20of%20the%20other%20projects%20%E2%80%94%20there%20are%2032%20of%20them%20at%20launch.%20All%20components%20come%20in%20a%20box%20with%20dedicated%20compartments%20for%20easy%20sorting%3B%20ensuring%20the%20pieces%20go%20back%20in%20the%20right%20place%20is%20also%20an%20educational%20lesson%2C%20as%20it%20teaches%20organization.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22lego%20spike%20prime%20hub%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5e1f98efb6d52d3ae575e027%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Hub%20is%20the%20brain%20and%20heart%20of%20all%20Spike%20Prime%20creations.%3Cp%3ELes%20Shu%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20program%20the%20Hub%20and%20the%20accompanying%20motors%20and%20sensors%2C%20you'd%20need%20to%20launch%20the%20Spike%20Prime%20app%20on%20a%20Mac%2C%20Windows%2C%20or%20Chromebook%20laptop%2C%20or%20an%20iOS%20or%20Android%20device%3B%20the%20Hub%20connects%20wirelessly%20using%20Bluetooth.%20At%20first%20launch%2C%20the%20app%20has%20a%20quick%20tutorial%20that%20guides%20you%20through%20the%20basics.%20The%20programming%20language%20is%20based%20on%20the%20Scratch%20coding%20platform%2C%20which%20is%20already%20taught%20in%20schools%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2032%20lessons%20start%20with%20something%20as%20simple%20as%20programming%20an%20emoji%20on%20the%20Hub's%20display%2C%20to%20more%20sophisticated%20builds%20like%20the%20aforementioned%20breakdancing%20robot.%20Each%20lesson%20guides%20you%20through%20the%20build%20%E2%80%94%20similar%20to%20the%20instruction%20booklet%20that%20comes%20with%20a%20Lego%20set.%20However%2C%20should%20the%20user%20get%20stuck%2C%20there%20is%20a%20troubleshoot%20panel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22lego%20spike%20prime%20coding%202%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5e1f992024306a3a637babd3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETo%20program%20Spike%20Prime%2C%20Lego%20uses%20a%20drag-and-drop%20computer%20coding%20language%20called%20Scratch.%3Cp%3ELes%20Shu%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20build%2C%20you%20can%20start%20programming.%20Scratch%20is%20a%20drag-and-drop%20system%20that%20lets%20you%20build%20a%20set%20of%20instructions.%20For%20example%2C%20you%20can%20determine%20how%20long%20and%20how%20fast%20to%20spin%20a%20motor%20that's%20connected%20to%20a%20particular%20port.%20Students%20who%20have%20experience%20with%20this%20type%20of%20coding%20will%20find%20it%20familiar%20and%20a%20breeze%2C%20while%20teachers%20and%20parents%20may%20need%20to%20spend%20some%20time%20getting%20acquainted.%20Yes%2C%20Spike%20Prime%20isn't%20just%20an%20educational%20tool%20for%20kids%2C%20but%20it%20can%20also%20teach%20adults%20about%20STEAM%20concepts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EPlaying%20with%20Spike%20Prime%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdmittedly%2C%20I%20don't%20have%20extensive%20experience%20with%20drag-and-drop%20coding%20platforms%2C%20but%20after%20an%20hour%20of%20tinkering%20and%20creating%20a%20couple%20builds%2C%20I%20got%20the%20hang%20of%20it.%20While%20the%20hunting-and-pecking%20for%20parts%20is%20part%20of%20the%20Lego%20building%20experience%2C%20I%20appreciate%20that%20the%20Spike%20Prime%20components%20are%20easy%20to%20find%20in%20their%20respective%20bins%20%E2%80%94%20that%20is%2C%20if%20they%20were%20put%20back%20correctly.%20The%20reason%20Lego%20created%20this%20organization%20system%20is%20to%20be%20mindful%20of%20classroom%20time%2C%20since%20some%20projects%20can%20last%20around%2045%20minutes%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20student.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22lego%20spike%20prime%20box%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5e1f99d5b6d52d3b9b31afb2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESpike%20Prime%20bricks%20and%20parts%20come%20organized.%3Cp%3ELes%20Shu%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20will%20be%20experimenting%20more%20with%20Spike%20Prime%20in%20the%20coming%20weeks%20and%20will%20update%20this%20review%20accordingly%2C%20but%20through%20the%20tutorials%2C%20I%20was%20able%20to%20get%20my%20mind%20around%20it%20quickly%20within%20an%20hour.%20Building%20the%20projects%20is%20straightforward%20for%20anyone%20who's%20played%20with%20Legos%2C%20but%20that's%20just%20half%20the%20%26quot%3Bfun%26quot%3B%2C%20since%20you'd%20still%20need%20to%20program%20it.%20Unlike%20computer%20programming%20languages%20that%20I%20grew%20up%20with%2C%20such%20as%20BASIC%2C%20CSS%2C%20and%20HTML%2C%20the%20drag-and-drop%20is%20much%20easier%20to%20grasp%3B%20although%20it%20can%20get%20complex%2C%20as%20I%20am%20looking%20forward%20to%20learning%20with%20more%20difficult%20projects%20down%20the%20line%20(note%3A%20you%20don't%20need%20prior%20experience%20with%20coding).%20And%2C%20it's%20fun%20to%20see%20your%20creations%20come%20alive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22lego%20spike%20prime%20hopper%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5e1f99f024306a3ae1428873%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20created%20and%20programmed%20this%20project%2C%20Hopper%2C%20in%20about%2010%20minutes.%3Cp%3ELes%20Shu%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBecause%20Spike%20Prime%20utilizes%20existing%20Lego%20and%20Technics%20blocks%2C%20I%20can%20imagine%20kids%2C%20after%20they've%20exhausted%20the%20projects%2C%20branching%20out%20on%20their%20own%20with%20new%20creations.%20In%20fact%2C%20Lego%20Education%20even%20offers%20an%20expansion%20pack%20(%2499.95)%20of%20603%20additional%20components%20that%20are%20designed%20to%20prepare%20kids%20for%20robotics%20competitions%2C%20like%20the%20First%20Lego%20League%20and%20World%20Robot%20Olympiad.%20Everything%20starts%20with%20the%20Hub%2C%20but%20you%20can%20easily%20build%20on%20top%20of%20it%20by%20using%20your%20own%20bricks.%20As%20I%20continue%20my%20STEAM%20education%2C%20I%20am%20interested%20in%20seeing%20how%20open%20the%20coding%20platform%20is%20for%20new%20creations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22lego%20spike%20prime%20expansion%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5e1f9a2fb6d52d3bdf354d85%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAn%20optional%20expansion%20pack%20teaches%20students%20to%20build%20competition-ready%20robots.%3Cp%3ELes%20Shu%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EContinuing%20education%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20Spike%20Prime's%20target%20audience%20is%20middle%20school%20kids%2C%20it's%20also%20a%20great%20tool%20for%20parents%20to%20become%20involved%20with%20their%20children's%20curriculum%20and%20learn%20a%20bit%20about%20coding%20and%20STEAM%20education.%20I%20can%20also%20see%20Spike%20Prime%20being%20a%20fun%20toy%20for%20geeks%2C%20Lego%20fans%2C%20or%20anyone%20who%20likes%20to%20tinker%20with%20tech.%20It's%20expensive%2C%20which%20is%20why%20Lego%20Education%20considers%20Spike%20Prime%20a%20classroom%20tool%20rather%20than%20a%20consumer%20product.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22lego%20spike%20prime%20rain%20or%20shine%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5e1f9a7e24306a3b3719aec5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOne%20of%20the%20more%20advanced%20Spike%20Prime%20projects%20is%20a%20robot%20that%20forecasts%20the%20weather.%3Cp%3ELes%20Shu%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15126321367hm-20%26h%3D86bf73f933f8d8951efe9d6d0ae15fe8839d07180cdd1799e06950da980f9eb7%26postID%3D61b8efc7f2a36b1ac9f42b83%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Ftech%252Flego-spike-prime-review%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fgo.skimresources.com%252F%253Fid%253D35871X943606%2526amp%253Bxs%253D1%2526amp%253Burl%253Dhttps%25253A%25252F%25252Feducation.lego.com%25252Fen-us%25252Fproducts%25252Flego-education-spike-prime-set%25252F45678%252523product%25253Ficmp%25253DLP-SHCC-MP-NO-educat-142%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESpike%20Prime%3C%2Fa%3E%20isn't%20Lego%20Education's%20first%20STEAM%20or%20robotics%20toy%2C%20but%20it's%20definitely%20the%20first%20that%20taps%20into%20today's%20classrooms.%20It%20also%20bridges%20education%20and%20fun%2C%20and%20judging%20from%20the%20kids'%20reactions%20I%20saw%20during%20Spike%20Prime's%20announcement%20last%20year%2C%20kids%20will%20be%20naturally%20drawn%20to%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Flego-spike-prime-review%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1776978663000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5e1f98c262fa8139db4562d5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.co