20more%20traditional%20health%20data%20points.%20The%20Halo%20band%20includes%20a%20microphone%20for%20listening%20to%20your%20voice%20and%20uses%20machine%20learning%20to%20assess%20whether%20you%20sound%20positive%2C%20energetic%2C%20tired%2C%20or%20annoyed%20among%20other%20moods.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20interesting%20to%20see%20a%20company%20like%20Amazon%20bring%20something%20new%20to%20the%20health%20and%20fitness%20space.%20And%20there%20are%20plenty%20of%20things%20Amazon%20gets%20right%20with%20the%20Halo%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20basic%20fitness%20tracking.%20But%20the%20features%20it%20developed%20to%20differentiate%20its%20fitness%20offering%20from%20those%20made%20by%20rivals%20like%20Apple%20and%20Fitbit%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20the%20tone%20analysis%20function%20%E2%80%94%20make%20me%20feel%20insecure%20rather%20than%20motivated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20always%20choose%20not%20to%20use%20the%20voice%20analysis%20feature%20and%20just%20wear%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiauto-40772-20%26h%3D3d1b6130cf735eab8b8e5078d08ecbd1a56699615ad7699bd1e6f60a31825611%26postID%3D61b8efc8f2a36b1ac9f431e4%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Ftech%252Famazon-halo-review%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FAmazon-Halo-Fitness-And-Health-Band%252Fdp%252FB07QKPCQKW%253F%2526amp%253BlinkCode%253Dll1%2526amp%253Btag%253Dbiip_022221_amazon-halo-review-20%2526amp%253BlinkId%253De3f4d5adb352291e6122ef82f2a883f9%2526amp%253Blanguage%253Den_US%2526amp%253Bref_%253Das_li_ss_tl%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHalo%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20a%20regular%20fitness%20tracker%2C%20of%20course.%20But%20that%20doesn't%20address%20the%20Halo's%20biggest%20drawback%2C%20in%20my%20opinion%2C%20which%20is%20that%20you%20need%20to%20pay%20%243.99%20per%20month%20after%20your%20first%20six%20months%20to%20get%20most%20of%20the%20Halo's%20features.That%20makes%20it%20hard%20to%20recommend%20over%20trackers%20like%20the%20Fitbit%20Inspire%202%2C%20which%20is%20less%20expensive%20and%20in%20some%20ways%20offers%20more%20functionality.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere's%20a%20closer%20look%20at%20what%20it's%20been%20like%20to%20use%20the%20Amazon%20Halo.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUpdated%20on%204%2F20%2F21%20by%20Lisa%20Eadicicco%3A%20Added%20details%20about%20Alexa%20integration%20with%20the%20Amazon%20Halo%20based%20on%20long%20term%20usage.%20This%20review%20was%20originally%20published%20on%202%2F22%2F21%20and%20our%20verdict%20has%20not%20changed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Faside%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3ETone%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20Amazon%20Halo's%20marquee%20features%20is%20its%20ability%20to%20analyze%20the%20tone%20of%20your%20voice.%20The%20capability%2C%20appropriately%20called%20Tone%2C%20can%20passively%20listen%20to%20your%20speech%20throughout%20the%20day%20and%20flag%20any%20notable%20moments%20at%20which%20you%20sounded%20particularly%20positive%20or%20negative.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20also%20choose%20to%20have%20it%20evaluate%20your%20voice%20in%20real%20time%2C%20or%20turn%20the%20feature%20off%20entirely%20by%20shutting%20off%20the%20band's%20microphone.%20Tone%20is%20designed%20to%20only%20recognize%20your%20voice%20and%20not%20those%20of%20the%20people%20around%20you.%20And%20you%20must%20set%20up%20the%20feature%20before%20using%20it%2C%20so%20it's%20completely%20voluntary.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20course%20of%20my%20review%2C%20I%20left%20the%20microphone%20on%20and%20allowed%20the%20band%20to%20monitor%20the%20tone%20of%20my%20voice%20throughout%20the%20day.%20Since%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiauto-40772-20%26h%3D3d1b6130cf735eab8b8e5078d08ecbd1a56699615ad7699bd1e6f60a31825611%26postID%3D61b8efc8f2a36b1ac9f431e4%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Ftech%252Famazon-halo-review%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FAmazon-Halo-Fitness-And-Health-Band%252Fdp%252FB07QKPCQKW%253F%2526amp%253BlinkCode%253Dll1%2526amp%253Btag%253Dbiip_022221_amazon-halo-review-20%2526amp%253BlinkId%253De3f4d5adb352291e6122ef82f2a883f9%2526amp%253Blanguage%253Den_US%2526amp%253Bref_%253Das_li_ss_tl%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHalo%20band%3C%2Fa%3E%20doesn't%20have%20a%20screen%2C%20the%20app%20serves%20as%20your%20window%20into%20your%20health%20metrics%2C%20including%20how%20you%20sound.%20The%20app's%20home%20screen%20greets%20you%20with%20a%20dashboard%20showing%20tiles%20for%20activity%20progress%2C%20sleep%20data%2C%20your%20tone%2C%20and%20body%20fat%20measurements.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETapping%20into%20those%20tiles%20lets%20you%20view%20more%20information%20about%20that%20metric%2C%20such%20as%20notable%20moments%20at%20which%20you%20sounded%20particularly%20positive%20or%20energetic%20as%20it%20applies%20to%20Tone.%20While%20it%20was%20insightful%20on%20some%20level%20to%20see%20how%20I%20sounded%20during%20different%20conversations%2C%20it%20also%20made%20me%20a%20bit%20paranoid.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20that%20I've%20been%20wearing%20the%20Halo%2C%20I%20often%20find%20myself%20checking%20the%20app%20after%20a%20work%20meeting%20or%20a%20social%20call%20with%20friends%20to%20see%20how%20I%20came%20across%20during%20the%20conversation.%20Apparently%2C%20I%20tend%20to%20sound%20more%20positive%20and%20energetic%20during%20work%20meetings%20(Halo%20uses%20words%20like%20%26quot%3Bwarm%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3Bappreciative%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bproud%26quot%3B%20to%20describe%20my%20tone)%2C%20while%20at%20times%20I%20sound%20irritated%20or%20dismissive%20in%20other%20conversations%20with%20friends%20or%20my%20husband.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Amazon%20Halo%20Tone%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6033e7e9bed5c50011a2bd73%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ELisa%20Eadicicco%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20couldn't%20help%20but%20question%20any%20interaction%20that%20Amazon%20had%20labeled%20as%20sounding%20irritated%20or%20tired.%20Who%20was%20I%20speaking%20to%3F%20What%20were%20we%20talking%20about%3F%20Is%20that%20what%20people%20think%20I%20sound%20like%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmazon%20says%20the%20point%20behind%20Tone%20is%20to%20help%20you%20be%20more%20mindful%20in%20how%20you%20sound%20when%20speaking%20to%20others%20to%20improve%20your%20personal%20relationships.%20Dr.%20Don%20Cole%2C%20clinical%20director%20for%20The%20Gottman%20Institute%2C%20which%20specializes%20in%20research-based%20relationship%20counseling%2C%20says%20there's%20value%20in%20understanding%20how%20you%20sound%20to%20others%20if%20there's%20something%20to%20be%20learned%20from%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20three%20minutes%20of%20a%20conversation%20are%20especially%20important%20because%20they%20often%20dictate%20how%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20conversation%20could%20play%20out%2C%20Dr.%20Cole%20said%20to%20Insider.%20As%20such%2C%20understanding%20how%20your%20tone%20comes%20across%20in%20the%20beginning%20of%20a%20conversation%20could%20be%20helpful%2C%20especially%20for%20couples%20going%20through%20conflict%2C%20according%20to%20Dr.%20Cole.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20it's%20important%20not%20to%20get%20too%20hung%20up%20on%20the%20results.%20Doing%20so%20could%20make%20it%20hard%20to%20establish%20a%20personal%20connection%20in%20the%20moment.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20you%20can%20spend%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20worrying%20about%2C%20or%20thinking%20about%2C%20those%20moments%20rather%20than%20just%20experiencing%20the%20interactions%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr.%20Cole%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20I%20think%20when%20we%20take%20ourselves%20out%20of%20the%20moment%2C%20sometimes%20there's%20loss%20there.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmazon%20also%20has%20wellness%20programs%20and%20workouts%20that%20can%20help%20you%20improve%20certain%20metrics%20and%20stay%20healthy.%20For%20the%20Tone%20metric%2C%20it%20has%20corresponding%20video%20programs%20that%20are%20meant%20to%20help%20you%20improve%20conversation%20and%20listening%20skills.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20for%20me%2C%20it%20was%20unclear%20how%20watching%20a%20short%20seminar%20on%20how%20to%20be%20a%20better%20listener%20would%20help%20me%20sound%20more%20positive%20and%20less%20irritated%20during%20conversations%20when%20I%20don't%20even%20know%20why%20my%20voice%20sounded%20that%20way%20to%20begin%20with.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EBody%20fat%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiauto-40772-20%26h%3D3d1b6130cf735eab8b8e5078d08ecbd1a56699615ad7699bd1e6f60a31825611%26postID%3D61b8efc8f2a36b1ac9f431e4%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Ftech%252Famazon-halo-review%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FAmazon-Halo-Fitness-And-Health-Band%252Fdp%252FB07QKPCQKW%253F%2526amp%253BlinkCode%253Dll1%2526amp%253Btag%253Dbiip_022221_amazon-halo-review-20%2526amp%253BlinkId%253De3f4d5adb352291e6122ef82f2a883f9%2526amp%253Blanguage%253Den_US%2526amp%253Bref_%253Das_li_ss_tl%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHalo%3C%2Fa%3E's%20other%20headlining%20feature%20is%20its%20ability%20to%20measure%20and%20track%20your%20body%20fat.%20Amazon%20does%20this%20by%20taking%20a%20scan%20of%20your%20body%20through%20your%20smartphone's%20camera%20and%20then%20generating%20a%203D%20avatar%20of%20your%20body%20and%20a%20body%20fat%20percentage%20through%20machine%20learning%20and%20computer%20vision.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmazon%20says%20it's%20nearly%20twice%20as%20accurate%20as%20leading%20smart%20home%20scales%20and%20comparable%20to%20methods%20a%20doctor%20would%20use%20in%20terms%20of%20accuracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20take%20a%20scan%2C%20you%20must%20first%20change%20into%20minimal%20clothing.%20And%20by%20minimal%20clothing.%20I%20mean%20practically%20nothing.%20For%20women%2C%20Amazon%20suggests%20wearing%20a%20bikini%20top%20and%20bottom%20or%20compression%20shorts%20with%20a%20bra%20or%20sports%20bra.%20After%20positioning%20the%20camera%20in%20the%20right%20place%2C%20the%20app%20will%20tell%20you%20to%20turn%20around%20a%20few%20times%20so%20that%20it%20can%20capture%20your%20full%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20scan%20is%20complete%2C%20Amazon%20generates%20a%20percentage%20and%203D%20avatar%20in%20seconds.%20For%20privacy%20purposes%2C%20Amazon%20deletes%20body%20scans%20from%20the%20cloud%20by%20default%20after%20they've%20been%20processed%20unless%20you%20choose%20to%20save%20them.%20You%20can%20also%20delete%20body%20scan%20data%20anytime%20on%20the%20Settings%20menu%20(which%20I%20did%20immediately).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ability%20to%20take%20a%20body%20fat%20scan%20from%20home%20on%20your%20smartphone%20is%20useful%20because%20it%20makes%20it%20easy%20to%20monitor%20changes%20in%20your%20body%20on%20a%20regular%20basis.%20That's%20according%20to%20Dr.%20Amy%20Lee%2C%20head%20of%20nutrition%20at%20dietary%20supplement%20maker%20Nucific%2C%20who%20specializes%20in%20weight%20control%20methods%20and%20recently%20spoke%20to%20Insider%20about%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiauto-40772-20%26h%3D3d1b6130cf735eab8b8e5078d08ecbd1a56699615ad7699bd1e6f60a31825611%26postID%3D61b8efc8f2a36b1ac9f431e4%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Ftech%252Famazon-halo-review%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FAmazon-Halo-Fitness-And-Health-Band%252Fdp%252FB07QKPCQKW%253F%2526amp%253BlinkCode%253Dll1%2526amp%253Btag%253Dbiip_022221_amazon-halo-review-20%2526amp%253BlinkId%253De3f4d5adb352291e6122ef82f2a883f9%2526amp%253Blanguage%253Den_US%2526amp%253Bref_%253Das_li_ss_tl%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHalo%3C%2Fa%3E's%20body%20scan%20technology.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Dr.%20Lee%20also%20said%20Halo%20users%20should%20take%20the%20results%20with%20a%20grain%20of%20salt%2C%20especially%20since%20it%20can%20be%20difficult%20for%20a%20system%20like%20this%20to%20fully%20understand%20nuanced%20differences%20in%20body%20composition.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Amazon%20Halo%20Body%20Scan%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6033e858bed5c50011a2bd78%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ELisa%20Eadicicco%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20results%20also%20depend%20on%20how%20carefully%20the%20user%20follows%20Amazon's%20directions%20when%20taking%20the%20scans.%20And%20data%20like%20this%20is%20only%20helpful%20if%20the%20user%20understands%20that%20it%20should%20be%20factored%20in%20with%20other%20data%20points%2C%20research%2C%20and%20conversations%20with%20your%20doctor%2C%20according%20to%20Dr.%20Lee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20other%20words%2C%20don't%20read%20too%20deeply%20into%20the%20single%20body%20fat%20percentage%20number%20that%20Amazon%20provides.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20doing%20this%20at%20home%2C%20and%20you%20have%20no%20baseline%20and%20education%20in%20nutrition%2C%20and%20you're%20focusing%20everything%20you're%20doing%20for%20the%20past%20week%20on%20the%20change%20of%20a%20number%20.%20.%20.%20you%20might%20find%20yourself%20going%20down%20%5Ba%5D%20rabbit%20hole%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr.%20Lee%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI'm%20exactly%20the%20type%20of%20person%20Dr.%20Lee%20described.%20When%20I%20saw%20my%20scan%20results%2C%20I%20immediately%20panicked%20and%20wondered%20why%20my%20doctor%20had%20never%20flagged%20my%20weight%20or%20body%20fat%20percentage%20to%20me%20as%20being%20problematic%20in%20the%20past.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20became%20fixated%20on%20the%20results%2C%20which%20was%20frustrating%20because%20I%20felt%20totally%20fine%20about%20my%20personal%20progress%20when%20it%20came%20to%20eating%20healthy%20and%20exercising%20regularly%20before%20taking%20the%20scan.%20Overall%2C%20the%20body%20fat%20percentage%20scan%20and%20Tone%20features%20left%20me%20feeling%20somewhat%20paranoid%20and%20a%20little%20insecure%20instead%20of%20motivating%20me.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20long%20as%20you're%20paying%20for%20the%20subscription%2C%20there%20are%20tools%20in%20the%20app%20to%20help%20you%20manage%20your%20exercise%2C%20diet%2C%20and%20mental%20wellbeing.%20But%20maintaining%20a%20healthy%20body%20weight%20and%20fat%20percentage%20is%20a%20complex%20task.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20without%20more%20guidance%20about%20which%20programs%20to%20start%20with%20and%20how%20to%20contextualize%20these%20results%2C%20it's%20hard%20to%20find%20this%20data%20to%20be%20useful%20or%20actionable.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20what%20I've%20learned%20from%20wearing%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiauto-40772-20%26h%3D3d1b6130cf735eab8b8e5078d08ecbd1a56699615ad7699bd1e6f60a31825611%26postID%3D61b8efc8f2a36b1ac9f431e4%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Ftech%252Famazon-halo-review%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FAmazon-Halo-Fitness-And-Health-Band%252Fdp%252FB07QKPCQKW%253F%2526amp%253BlinkCode%253Dll1%2526amp%253Btag%253Dbiip_022221_amazon-halo-review-20%2526amp%253BlinkId%253De3f4d5adb352291e6122ef82f2a883f9%2526amp%253Blanguage%253Den_US%2526amp%253Bref_%253Das_li_ss_tl%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHalo%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20that%20I'm%20not%20in%20the%20healthy%20range%20of%20body%20fat%20percentage%2C%20but%20I'm%20a%20highly%20active%20person%20based%20on%20my%20Activity%20Score%20(more%20on%20that%20below).%20That%20felt%20like%20a%20confusing%20message%20to%20me%2C%20so%20I%20wish%20I%20had%20more%20information%20about%20why%20that%20might%20be%20the%20case%20or%20what%20to%20do%20next.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EFitness%20tracking%20and%20other%20features%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20one%20way%20Amazon%20has%20improved%20the%20fitness%20tracking%20experience%3A%20the%20way%20it%20tallies%20activity%20points.%20Rather%20than%20setting%20goals%20on%20a%20daily%20basis%20for%20calories%20burned%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiauto-40772-20%26h%3D3d1b6130cf735eab8b8e5078d08ecbd1a56699615ad7699bd1e6f60a31825611%26postID%3D61b8efc8f2a36b1ac9f431e4%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Ftech%252Famazon-halo-review%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FAmazon-Halo-Fitness-And-Health-Band%252Fdp%252FB07QKPCQKW%253F%2526amp%253BlinkCode%253Dll1%2526amp%253Btag%253Dbiip_022221_amazon-halo-review-20%2526amp%253BlinkId%253De3f4d5adb352291e6122ef82f2a883f9%2526amp%253Blanguage%253Den_US%2526amp%253Bref_%253Das_li_ss_tl%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHalo%3C%2Fa%3E%20monitors%20your%20activity%20on%20a%20weekly%20basis.%20You%20earn%20points%20for%20every%20minute%20you%20move%2C%20with%20intense%20activity%20counting%20for%20two%20points%20per%20minute%20while%20moderate%20and%20light%20activity%20will%20get%20you%20one%20point%20per%20minute.%20It%20also%20deducts%20points%20when%20you're%20too%20sedentary%20for%20long%20periods%20of%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20weekly%20goal%20is%20set%20at%20150%20activity%20points%2C%20which%20Amazon%20says%20is%20the%20right%20range%20for%20maintaining%20a%20healthy%20heart%20citing%20the%20American%20Heart%20Association.%20If%20you%20hit%20300%20points%2C%20you're%20considered%20to%20be%20very%20active.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Amazon%20Halo%20Activity%20Tracker%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6033e8a538aa9f00185e0389%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ELisa%20Eadicicco%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20like%20this%20system%20because%20in%20some%20ways%2C%20it%20feels%20more%20encouraging%20than%20living%20by%20daily%20goals.%20I'm%20usually%20a%20religious%20Apple%20Watch%20wearer%2C%20and%20it's%20made%20me%20obsessed%20with%20closing%20at%20least%20two%20of%20my%20rings%20every%20day%20if%20not%20all%20three.%20If%20I%20don't%20have%20time%20for%20a%20full%20workout%2C%20sometimes%20I%20find%20that%20I%20won't%20be%20active%20at%20all%20because%20I%20know%20that%20any%20hope%20of%20closing%20my%20Move%20Ring%20%E2%80%94%20the%20circular%20meter%20that%20fills%20up%20with%20calories%20burned%20from%20daily%20activity%20%E2%80%94%20is%20totally%20gone.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20Halo's%20weekly%20goals%20motivate%20me%20to%20move%20at%20least%20a%20little%20bit%20every%20day%20even%20when%20I'm%20not%20committing%20to%20a%20full%20workout.%20Taking%20a%20brisk%2020-minute%20walk%20feels%20more%20productive%20when%20I%20know%20it's%20going%20to%20contribute%20to%20my%20weekly%20goal%20compared%20to%20the%20Apple%20Watch%2C%20where%20it%20feels%20like%20that%20activity%20just%20falls%20into%20a%20black%20hole%20if%20it%20doesn't%20get%20me%20to%20my%20daily%20goal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiauto-40772-20%26h%3D3d1b6130cf735eab8b8e5078d08ecbd1a56699615ad7699bd1e6f60a31825611%26postID%3D61b8efc8f2a36b1ac9f431e4%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Ftech%252Famazon-halo-review%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FAmazon-Halo-Fitness-And-Health-Band%252Fdp%252FB07QKPCQKW%253F%2526amp%253BlinkCode%253Dll1%2526amp%253Btag%253Dbiip_022221_amazon-halo-review-20%2526amp%253BlinkId%253De3f4d5adb352291e6122ef82f2a883f9%2526amp%253Blanguage%253Den_US%2526amp%253Bref_%253Das_li_ss_tl%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHalo%3C%2Fa%3E%20also%20works%20well%20as%20a%20sleep%20tracker%20since%20it's%20light%20and%20comfortable%20enough%20to%20wear%20overnight.%20But%20more%20importantly%2C%20it%20provides%20a%20relatively%20comprehensive%20set%20of%20data%20about%20your%20sleep%2C%20even%20scoring%20the%20quality%20of%20your%20sleep%20much%20like%20Fitbit%20does.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20wearing%20the%20watch%20to%20bed%2C%20the%20Halo%20app%20will%20issue%20a%20score%20that%20indicates%20the%20quality%20of%20your%20sleep%20as%20well%20as%20how%20much%20time%20you%20spent%20asleep%2C%20how%20long%20it%20took%20you%20to%20fall%20asleep%2C%20the%20time%20you%20spent%20awake%2C%20and%20how%20much%20time%20you%20spent%20in%20REM%2C%20light%2C%20and%20deep%20sleep.%20That's%20much%20more%20thorough%20than%20the%20Apple%20Watch's%20sleep%20metrics%2C%20which%20basically%20just%20tell%20you%20the%20duration%20of%20your%20sleep.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmazon%20also%20offers%20a%20series%20of%20health%20programs%20under%20the%20Discover%20tab%20on%20the%20Halo%20app%2C%20which%20features%20videos%20based%20on%20partnerships%20with%20Exhale%2C%20Orangetheory%2C%20and%20many%20others%20that%20make%20it%20easy%20to%20jump%20into%20a%20workout%20or%20wellness%20exercise%20straight%20from%20your%20phone.%20You%20can%20filter%20these%20videos%20based%20on%20the%20type%20of%20workout%2C%20duration%2C%20difficulty%2C%20and%20the%20content%20provider.%20Unfortunately%2C%20though%2C%20you%20can't%20filter%20these%20workouts%20by%20whether%20or%20not%20they%20require%20equipment%2C%20which%20is%20particularly%20important%20now%20that%20many%20people%20are%20exercising%20at%20home.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20since%20Amazon%20encrypts%20your%20health%20data%2C%20which%20is%20great%20for%20privacy%2C%20you%20must%20factory%20reset%20and%20re-pair%20your%20band%20with%20a%20new%20device%20anytime%20you%20want%20to%20access%20your%20account%20elsewhere.%20While%20I'm%20glad%20Amazon%20is%20taking%20the%20appropriate%20steps%20to%20secure%20your%20health%20data%2C%20this%20also%20makes%20it%20difficult%20to%20access%20these%20workout%20videos%20since%20I%20need%20to%20re-pair%20my%20band%20with%20a%20different%20device%20each%20time%20I%20want%20to%20view%20a%20workout%20on%20a%20larger%20screen.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20I%20wish%20Amazon%20would%20at%20least%20make%20its%20Discover%20programs%20accessible%20on%20other%20devices%20upon%20logging%20in%20without%20carrying%20over%20the%20rest%20of%20your%20health%20data.%20Amazon%20suggests%20wirelessly%20casting%20workouts%20to%20a%20larger%20screen%20from%20your%20phone%20via%20AirPlay%20as%20a%20workaround.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20most%20of%20these%20features%20require%20Amazon's%20%243.99%20monthly%20subscription.%20Without%20that%2C%20you%20only%20get%20access%20to%20features%20like%20steps%2C%20heart%20rate%20data%2C%20calories%20burned%2C%20and%20the%20ability%20to%20log%20activity%20through%20the%20activity%20sessions%20feature.%20You%20also%20only%20get%20basic%20sleep%20data%20like%20the%20time%20you've%20spent%20asleep%20and%20awake%2C%20and%20your%20temperature%20while%20sleeping.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYou%20lose%20the%20Activity%20Score%2C%20which%20was%20one%20of%20my%20favorite%20things%20about%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiauto-40772-20%26h%3D3d1b6130cf735eab8b8e5078d08ecbd1a56699615ad7699bd1e6f60a31825611%26postID%3D61b8efc8f2a36b1ac9f431e4%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Ftech%252Famazon-halo-review%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FAmazon-Halo-Fitness-And-Health-Band%252Fdp%252FB07QKPCQKW%253F%2526amp%253BlinkCode%253Dll1%2526amp%253Btag%253Dbiip_022221_amazon-halo-review-20%2526amp%253BlinkId%253De3f4d5adb352291e6122ef82f2a883f9%2526amp%253Blanguage%253Den_US%2526amp%253Bref_%253Das_li_ss_tl%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHalo%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20as%20well%20as%20features%20like%20Tone%2C%20Body%20Fat%2C%20Activity%20Intensity%20(which%20rates%20the%20intensity%20of%20your%20activity)%2C%20Sleep%20Score%2C%20Sleep%20Stages%2C%20and%20Insights%2C%20which%20highlight%20trends%20and%20patterns%20in%20your%20health%20and%20fitness%20data%20over%20time.%20Discover%20programs%20are%20also%20limited%20without%20a%20subscription.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Amazon%20Halo%20Sleep%20Tracker%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6033e8e7bed5c50011a2bd7d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ELisa%20Eadicicco%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere's%20also%20no%20way%20to%20manage%20or%20cancel%20your%20membership%20from%20within%20the%20app.%20Instead%2C%20the%20app%20says%20you%20should%20visit%20the%20Your%20Membership%20%26amp%3B%20Subscriptions%20section%20of%20the%20Amazon%20app.%20A%20company%20spokesperson%20told%20Insider%20in%20February%20when%20this%20review%20was%20originally%20published%20that%20it%20planned%20to%20add%20a%20link%20that%20takes%20customers%20to%20the%20appropriate%20page%20for%20managing%20their%20membership.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20unusual%20for%20companies%20to%20put%20some%20fitness%20tracking%20features%20behind%20a%20subscription%20paywall.%20Fitbit%20does%20this%20too%20through%20its%20Fitbit%20Premium%20service.%20But%20Fitbit%20still%20offers%20analysis%20of%20sleep%20and%20REM%20sleep%20in%20its%20free%20tier%2C%20and%20it%20just%20recently%20made%20its%20Health%20Metrics%20dashboard%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2021%2F2%2F10%2F22276338%2Ffitbit-update-charge-4-health-metrics%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eavailable%20to%20non-Premium%20subscribers%3C%2Fa%3E.%20And%20since%20Fitbit's%20trackers%20include%20a%20screen%20and%20can%20deliver%20smartphone%20notifications%2C%20they%20still%20offer%20more%20functionality%20for%20the%20price%20comparatively.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EEase%20of%20use%20and%20battery%20life%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Amazon%20Halo%20is%20easy%20to%20get%20started%20with%2C%20and%20the%20setup%20process%20is%20very%20similar%20to%20that%20of%20other%20smartwatches%20and%20fitness%20bands.%20Just%20download%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiauto-40772-20%26h%3D3d1b6130cf735eab8b8e5078d08ecbd1a56699615ad7699bd1e6f60a31825611%26postID%3D61b8efc8f2a36b1ac9f431e4%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Ftech%252Famazon-halo-review%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FAmazon-Halo-Fitness-And-Health-Band%252Fdp%252FB07QKPCQKW%253F%2526amp%253BlinkCode%253Dll1%2526amp%253Btag%253Dbiip_022221_amazon-halo-review-20%2526amp%253BlinkId%253De3f4d5adb352291e6122ef82f2a883f9%2526amp%253Blanguage%253Den_US%2526amp%253Bref_%253Das_li_ss_tl%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHalo%3C%2Fa%3E%20app%2C%20put%20the%20band%20on%20its%20charger%2C%20and%20follow%20the%20instructions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMy%20biggest%20concern%20about%20the%20Halo's%20usability%20is%20the%20intentional%20design%20decision%20Amazon%20made%20to%20not%20include%20a%20screen%20on%20its%20fitness%20band.%20Amazon%20says%20this%20to%20prevent%20the%20band%20from%20becoming%20a%20distraction%20and%20taking%20away%20from%20the%20Halo's%20primary%20purpose%20of%20serving%20as%20a%20discrete%2C%20comfortable%20health%20monitoring%20device.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20I%20feel%20like%20Amazon%20could%20have%20achieved%20this%20goal%20without%20omitting%20a%20screen%20entirely.%20Wearing%20a%20device%20on%20your%20wrist%20that%20doesn't%20even%20tell%20the%20time%20feels%20like%20a%20missed%20opportunity.%20I%20would%20have%20preferred%20if%20the%20Halo%20had%20a%20small%20screen%20that%20only%20displayed%20the%20time%20and%20how%20many%20activity%20points%20you've%20achieved%20for%20the%20week%20without%20any%20notifications.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI'd%20even%20argue%20that%20requiring%20me%20to%20check%20my%20phone%20to%20see%20my%20stats%20is%20more%20distracting%2C%20since%20I'm%20likely%20to%20fall%20down%20the%20rabbit%20hole%20of%20check%20email%20and%20Twitter%20when%20picking%20up%20my%20phone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmazon%20does%20have%20an%20alternative%20if%20you%20don't%20want%20to%20check%20your%20phone%3A%20Just%20ask%20Alexa.%20The%20company%20launched%20Alexa%20integration%20for%20the%20Halo%20in%20March%2C%20meaning%20you%20can%20ask%20Amazon's%20digital%20helper%20for%20information%20about%20your%20activity%2C%20tone%2C%20sleep%2C%20and%20more.%20The%20feature%20is%20off%20by%20default%2C%20and%20you%20can%20choose%20to%20protect%20any%20health-related%20questions%20with%20a%20PIN.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlexa's%20usefulness%20depends%20on%20how%20comfortable%20you%20are%20with%20Amazon's%20virtual%20assistant%20having%20access%20to%20your%20health%20data.%20But%20Amazon%20isn't%20the%20only%20tech%20giant%20offering%20this%20type%20of%20integration%3B%20the%20Google%20Assistant%20on%20Google's%20new%20sleep-sensing%20Nest%20Hub%20can%20also%20tell%20you%20information%20about%20your%20sleep%20when%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI've%20used%20Alexa%20to%20check%20in%20on%20my%20activity%20progress%20for%20the%20day.%20But%20I'd%20much%20rather%20have%20Alexa%20built%20into%20the%20band%20itself%20so%20that%20I%20could%20use%20it%20to%20set%20timers%20and%20alarms%20during%20workouts%20like%20I%20do%20with%20the%20Apple%20Watch.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmazon's%20fitness%20tracker%20can%20last%20for%20a%20decently%20long%20time%20on%20a%20single%20charge%2C%20which%20makes%20it%20great%20for%20sleep%20tracking.%20I%20got%20a%20little%20more%20than%20two%20days%20worth%20of%20battery%20life%20out%20of%20the%20Halo%2C%20but%20it%20would%20probably%20last%20longer%20if%20you%20have%20the%20microphone%20turned%20off%20and%20aren't%20using%20the%20Tone%20feature.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EShould%20you%20buy%20it%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Amazon%20Halo%20Band%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6033e922bed5c50011a2bd81%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ELisa%20Eadicicco%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERegardless%20of%20your%20opinion%20on%20the%20Halo's%20Tone%20feature%20and%20its%20body%20fat%20measurements%2C%20there%20are%20more%20capable%20options%20out%20there%20for%20those%20in%20search%20of%20a%20simple%20and%20affordable%20fitness%20tracker.%20Although%20I%20like%20Amazon's%20approach%20to%20activity%20tracking%20and%20appreciate%20the%20Halo's%20comprehensive%20sleep%20tracking%20capabilities%2C%20there%20are%20too%20many%20drawbacks%20to%20consider.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiauto-40772-20%26h%3D3d1b6130cf735eab8b8e5078d08ecbd1a56699615ad7699bd1e6f60a31825611%26postID%3D61b8efc8f2a36b1ac9f431e4%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Ftech%252Famazon-halo-review%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FAmazon-Halo-Fitness-And-Health-Band%252Fdp%252FB07QKPCQKW%253F%2526amp%253BlinkCode%253Dll1%2526amp%253Btag%253Dbiip_022221_amazon-halo-review-20%2526amp%253BlinkId%253De3f4d5adb352291e6122ef82f2a883f9%2526amp%253Blanguage%253Den_US%2526amp%253Bref_%253Das_li_ss_tl%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHalo%3C%2Fa%3E's%20lack%20of%20a%20screen%20and%20the%20fact%20that%20you%20have%20to%20pay%20%243.99%20per%20month%20after%20the%20first%20six%20months%20to%20get%20the%20best%20features%2C%20like%20Activity%20Score%2C%20make%20it%20tough%20to%20recommend.%20Yes%2C%20Fitbit%20also%20requires%20a%20subscription%20to%20access%20advanced%20features%2C%20but%20it%20still%20offers%20more%20detailed%20sleep%20data%20in%20its%20free%20tier%20compared%20to%20Amazon.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EWhat%20are%20your%20alternatives%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFitbit's%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiauto-40772-20%26h%3D54a44814a920818aceb4505f2491ef04b835815361a942005805e6a8ee3dc135%26postID%3D61b8efc8f2a36b1ac9f431e4%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Ftech%252Famazon-halo-review%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.anrdoezrs.net%252Flinks%252F6415797%252Ftype%252Fdlg%252Fhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.fitbit.com%252Fglobal%252Fus%252Fproducts%252Ftrackers%252Finspire2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInspire%202%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20is%20currently%20available%20for%20%2469.95%2C%20is%20a%20solid%20choice%20if%20you're%20looking%20for%20an%20inexpensive%20and%20basic%20fitness%20tracker.%20It%20monitors%20metrics%20like%20sleep%2C%20calorie%20burn%2C%20activity%2C%20and%20heart%20rate%2C%20lasts%20for%20more%20than%20a%20week%20on%20a%20single%20charge%2C%20and%20reminds%20you%20to%20move%20when%20you're%20too%20sedentary.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20comes%20with%20a%20free%20one-year%20trial%20for%20Fitbit%20Premium%2C%20whereas%20the%20Amazon%20Halo%20only%20comes%20with%20a%20si