%3D%5C%22Carcassone%20board%20game%20correct%20tile%20placement%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F616d80fc38c1960018305357%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222888%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJoe%20Osborne%2FInsider%20Reviews%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20a%20player's%20next%20round%2C%20they%20can%20lay%20another%20tile%20or%20place%20one%20meeple%20on%20the%20tile%20that%20was%20last%20placed%2C%20provided%20that%20the%20tile%20has%20an%20image%20of%20a%20road%20or%20city%3B%20this%20is%20how%20a%20player%20builds%20control%20of%20a%20territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAs%20turns%20pass%2C%20you%20can%20build%20out%20that%20road%20or%20city%20with%20tile%20placements%20that%20make%20sense.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222572%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Carcassone%20board%20game%20turn%20four%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F616d812738c1960018305362%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221929%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJoe%20Osborne%2FInsider%20Reviews%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20complete%2C%20you'll%20earn%20points%20for%20the%20amount%20of%20tiles%20used%3A%20roads%20are%20worth%20one%20point%20per%20tile%2C%20cities%20are%20worth%20two%20(cities%20with%20a%20crest%20icon%20are%20worth%20four)%2C%20and%20fields%20are%20worth%20no%20points.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EHere's%20where%20things%20get%20challenging%3A%20All%20players%20have%20the%20option%20of%20placing%20their%20own%20drawn%20tiles%20next%20to%20tiles%20other%20players%20have%20already%20claimed.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222995%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Carcassone%20board%20game%20turn%20five%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F616d81b638c1960018305383%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222246%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJoe%20Osborne%2FInsider%20Reviews%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20action%20contests%20the%20other%20player's%20claim%20for%20either%20a%20city%20or%20a%20road.%20The%20winner%20of%20the%20tile%20points%20is%20the%20player%20with%20the%20most%20meeples%20on%20the%20city%20or%20road%20being%20scored.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThis%2C%20of%20course%2C%20drives%20the%20strategy%20of%20the%20game%2C%20and%20I've%20seen%20many%20archetypes%20of%20players%20since%20playing%20Carcassonne%20for%20at%20least%20five%20years%20now.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223100%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Carcassone%20board%20game%20turn%20six%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F616d826338c19600183053a7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222325%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJoe%20Osborne%2FInsider%20Reviews%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20aggressive%20players%20who%20try%20to%20challenge%20every%20territory%20feature%20in%20progress%20that%20they%20come%20across.%20There%20are%20passive%20players%20who%20just%20try%20to%20complete%20their%20little%20fiefdoms%20unnoticed%20%E2%80%94%20and%20there%20are%20players%2C%20like%20myself%2C%20who%20go%20for%20massive%20wins%20with%20multi-tile%20mega-structures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20game%20ends%20when%20there%20are%20no%20more%20board%20tiles%20to%20be%20drawn.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222483%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Carcassone%20board%20game%20turn%20seven%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F616d831441af0d00193f0e78%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221862%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJoe%20Osborne%2FInsider%20Reviews%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20remaining%20road%20and%20city%20tiles%20still%20in%20progress%20are%20scored%20to%20determine%20the%20winner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWhat%20I%20love%20about%20Carcassonne%20is%20how%20fresh%20every%20game%20session%20feels%2C%20thanks%20to%20the%20randomized%20board.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223187%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Carcassone%20board%20game%20with%20scoring%20board%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F616d840538c1960018305417%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222390%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJoe%20Osborne%2FInsider%20Reviews%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20enjoy%20how%20many%20options%20are%20available%20in%20each%20turn%20just%20from%20two%20actions%2C%20drawing%20a%20tile%20and%20placing%20a%20meeple%2C%20and%20all%20of%20the%20strategic%20decisions%20that%20are%20possible%20with%20just%20those%20two%20options%20per%20turn.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EEven%20better%20is%20that%20the%20core%20game%20box%20includes%20an%20expansion%20set%20of%20tiles%20that%20include%20a%20river%20feature%20that%20narrows%20the%20game's%20strategy%20in%20on%20the%20river%20tiles.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Carcassone%20board%20game%20in%20play%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F616d848338c196001830543c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJoe%20Osborne%2FInsider%20Reviews%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20enhanced%20element%20mixes%20up%20the%20decisions%20players%20can%20make%20as%20they%20now%20have%20to%20consider%20this%20river.%20Then%2C%20when%20you%20get%20bored%20of%20that%2C%20you%20can%20purchase%20additional%20expansion%20sets%20that%20build%20upon%20the%20core%20game%2C%20such%20as%20The%20Princess%20and%20the%20Dragon%2C%20which%20sees%20players%20staving%20off%20a%20dragon%20attack%20and%20rescuing%20a%20princess.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20indisputably%20an%20incredible%20amount%20of%20game%20here%20that%20should%20make%20a%20convert%20out%20of%20anyone%20who%20plays%20with%20an%20open%20mind.%20Carcassonne%20is%20available%20at%20the%20time%20of%20writing%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.in