er.com%2F5f6222a557b7da001ee11ef7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EInstax%20square%20photos%20have%20an%20image%20area%20of%202.4%20by%202.4%20inches.%3Cp%3ELes%20Shu%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20more%20common%20Instax%20instant%20film%20you'll%20see%20is%20the%20Instax%20Mini%2C%20which%20measures%202.1%20by%203.4%20inches%20%E2%80%94%20roughly%20the%20size%20of%20a%20standard%20business%20card%20%E2%80%94%20with%20an%20image%20area%20of%201.8%20by%202.4%20inches%2C%20and%20is%20used%20by%20most%20Instax%20cameras.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20in%202017%2C%20Fujifilm%20launched%20its%20first%20square%20film%2C%20measuring%202.8%20by%203.4%20inches%20with%20an%20image%20area%20of%202.4%20by%202.4%20inches.%20While%20the%20instant%20technology%20is%20the%20same%2C%20the%20square%20film%20lets%20you%20capture%20more%20in%20the%20picture%20and%20create%20more%20background%20blur.%20It%20is%20also%20reminiscent%20of%20Polaroid%20instant%20film%2C%20albeit%20smaller%20(Polaroid%20is%203%20by%203%20inches).%20In%20my%20opinion%2C%20the%20square%20film%20looks%20better%20when%20framed%20or%20stuck%20to%20a%20wall.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20SQ1%20is%20the%20fourth%20Instax%20camera%20to%20use%20the%20square%20film%20(besides%20the%20SQ6%2C%20there%20are%20two%20digital-analog%20hybrid%20models%2C%20the%20SQ10%20and%20SQ20).%20Despite%20the%20larger%20dimensions%20of%20the%20film%2C%20the%20overall%20size%20of%20the%20camera%20isn't%20that%20much%20bigger%20than%20Instax%20Mini%20cameras.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22fujifilm%20instax%20sq1%20review%206%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5f6225e857b7da001ee11f0e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELoading%20film%20is%20easy%3A%20Just%20open%20the%20back%20cover%20and%20drop-in%20the%20film%20cartridge.%20However%2C%20make%20sure%20it's%20on%20the%20correct%20side.%3Cp%3ELes%20Shu%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20launch%20of%20the%20SQ1%2C%20Fujifilm%20is%20introducing%20two%20new%20film%20options%2C%20one%20with%20a%20rainbow%20border%20and%20a%20monochrome%20film.%20If%20you're%20into%20black-and-white%20photography%2C%20the%20monochrome%20film%20is%20one%20to%20watch.%20Unfortunately%2C%20it%20wasn't%20available%20during%20my%20review%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFilm%20is%20where%20things%20get%20costly.%20A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15126320047bs-20%26h%3D095ce1646d5209b942f41bfba60ac8f91118d8236eb6b87d133a6cfa898d6dbc%26postID%3D61b8efc8f2a36b1ac9f42f92%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Ftech%252Ffujifilm-instax-square-sq1-instant-camera-review%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fbestbuy.7tiv.net%252Fc%252F196318%252F614286%252F10014%253Fu%253Dhttps%25253A%25252F%25252Fwww.bestbuy.com%25252Fsite%25252Ffujifilm-instax-square-twin-film-20-sheets-black-frame%25252F6282913.p%25253FskuId%25253D6282913%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etwin-pack%20of%2010%20Instax%20square%20film%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20approximately%20%2420%2C%20while%20specialty%20film%20cost%20around%20%2415%20for%20just%2010.%20Instant%20photography%20is%20fun%2C%20but%20there%20is%20a%20high%20cost%20of%20ownership%20if%20you're%20trigger-happy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EIt's%20not%20a%20nostalgia%20product%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20consumer%20instant%20camera%20dates%20back%20to%20the%20late%201940s%2C%20with%20the%20introduction%20of%20Polaroid's%20Land%20Camera.%20While%20instant%20photography%20has%20often%20been%20thought%20of%20as%20legacy%20technology%20from%20a%20bygone%20era%2C%20the%20Instax%20SQ1%20%E2%80%94%20and%20most%20Instax%20cameras%20from%20the%20past%20few%20years%20%E2%80%94is%20actually%20designed%20to%20be%20a%20new%20product%20for%20millennials%20and%20Gen-Z%20in%20particular.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFujifilm%20has%20had%20success%20with%20Instax%20thanks%20to%20newfound%20interest%20from%20the%20millennial%20generation.%20Like%20vinyl%20records%2C%20analog%20instant%20photography%20is%20decidedly%20%26quot%3Bnew%2C%26quot%3B%20original%2C%20physically%20shareable%2C%20and%20cool%2C%20as%20compared%20to%20the%20sameness%20of%20digital%20photography%20and%20social%20media.%20This%20is%20also%20attributed%20to%20the%20success%20of%20Zink%20instant%20film%20technology%20and%20the%20revival%20of%20the%20original%20Polaroid.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20Fujifilm's%20Instax%20business%20has%20become%20more%20profitable%20than%20its%20digital%20cameras%2C%20thanks%20to%20the%20company's%20early%20reinvestment%20in%20the%20technology%20and%20marketing%20it%20as%20a%20toy%20camera%20for%20a%20new%20generation.%20Fujifilm%20claims%20Instax%20sales%20in%202019%20were%20strong%2C%20and%20it's%20now%20looking%20to%20capture%20the%20Gen-Z%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20evident%20in%20the%20SQ1's%20colors.%20As%20mentioned%20earlier%2C%20the%20body%20colors%20pop%20and%20are%20more%20expressive%2C%20and%20it's%20as%20easy%20to%20use%20as%20a%20smartphone%20camera.%20In%20comparison%2C%20the%20previous%20SQ6%20comes%20in%20darker%2C%20metallic%20colors%20that%20can%20be%20considered%20more%20sophisticated%20and%2C%20perhaps%2C%20adult.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EThe%20bottom%20line%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22fujifilm%20instax%20sq1%20review%201%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5f62268c57b7da001ee11f16%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ELes%20Shu%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20SQ1%20may%20be%20targeted%20toward%20younger%20generations%2C%20but%20it's%20also%20a%20fun%20camera%20for%20anyone%20who%20appreciates%20film%20photography.%20Those%20of%20us%20who%20grew%20up%20with%20a%20Polaroid%20camera%20probably%20remember%20the%20thrill%20of%20taking%20pictures%20and%20seeing%20them%20developed%20in%20front%20of%20our%20eyes.%20The%20SQ1%20certainly%20brings%20back%20some%20of%20that%20nostalgia%20while%20introducing%20the%20medium%20to%20a%20new%20group%20of%20users.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20I%20wish%20Fujifilm%20retained%20some%20of%20the%20user-adjustable%20settings%2C%20the%20improved%20autoexposure%20system%20and%20ease%20of%20use%20are%20big%20improvements%20over%20the%20previous%20SQ6.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3EShould%20you%20buy%20it%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20what%20it%20is%2C%20it's%20a%20pricey%20camera%20that's%20also%20costly%20to%20maintain%20in%20terms%20of%20film.%20But%20it's%20unique%20and%20offers%20a%20more%20intimate%20experience%20that%20your%20smartphone%20can't%20produce.%20It%20lets%20you%20share%20photos%20physically%2C%20and%20it%20forces%20you%20to%20offload%20a%20photo%20rather%20than%20hiding%20it%20away%20in%20some%20digital%20graveyard.%20Whether%20you%20buy%20it%20will%20depend%20on%20your%20photography%20needs%2C%20but%20it%20does%20make%20a%20fun%20gift.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20price%20is%20a%20concern%2C%20check%20out%20the%20older%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15126320047bs-20%26h%3Da1450d4deb7d4390e4900df669643d769d5f3754ac5f86b49a02a87a1eb0431d%26postID%3D61b8efc8f2a36b1ac9f42f92%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Ftech%252Ffujifilm-instax-square-sq1-instant-camera-review%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.bhphotovideo.com%252Fc%252Fproduct%252F1438865-REG%252Ffujifilm_16608701_instax_square_sq6_ruby.html%252FBI%252F20673%252FKBID%252F15977%252FDFF%252Fd10-v21-t1-x922981%252FSID%252Fbiip_091720_fujifilm-instax-square-sq1-instant-camera-review%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESQ