20series%2C%20new%20movies%20from%20WarnerMedia%2C%20tons%20of%20kids%20content%2C%20easy%20to%20navigate%20app%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECons%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20A%20bit%20more%20expensive%20than%20other%20streaming%20services%2C%20lack%20of%204K%20playback%20is%20disappointing%20for%20new%20releases%2C%20only%20a%20small%20assortment%20of%20Max%20Originals%20so%20far%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fhbo-max-review%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1776978217000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5ed63357988ee37cc520ac33%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fhbo-max-review%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22HBO%20Max%20combines%20HBO's%20hit%20originals%20shows%20with%20newly%20released%20films.%20Its%20premium%20price%20is%20a%20bit%20high%2C%20but%20it%20offers%20a%20good%20value%20for%20moviegoers.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Kevin%20Webb)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%228%20effective%20and%20creative%20ways%20to%20learn%20a%20new%20language%20as%20an%20adult%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finsiderpicks%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EInsider%20Picks%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%C2%A0team%20writes%20about%20stuff%20we%20think%20you'll%20like.%20Business%20Insider%20has%20affiliate%20partnerships%20so%20we%20may%20get%20a%20share%20of%20the%20revenue%20from%20your%20purchase.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222667%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Babbel_Cafe_Nexus6_Dialogue_ENGSPA%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F598a034a76084a30198b50a2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EBabbel%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20excuses%20for%20not%20learning%20a%20second%20language%2C%20especially%20as%20an%20adult.%20Many%20of%20us%20know%20the%20oft-repeated%20adage%20that%20children%20under%20the%20age%20of%207%20are%20best-equipped%20to%20pick%20up%20a%20new%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20before%20you%20lead%20your%20whole%20life%20believing%20that%20you%E2%80%99ve%20missed%20your%20window%2C%20you%20might%20want%20to%20take%20a%20glance%20at%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fjournals.plos.org%2Fplosone%2Farticle%3Fid%3D10.1371%2Fjournal.pone.0013648%23s3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%202010%20study%20that%20found%20adults%20were%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20the%20superior%20language%20learners%3C%2Fa%3E.%20And%20after%20watching%20multiple%20TED%20talks%20given%20by%20polyglots%20on%20language%20learning%2C%20it%20seems%20most%20of%20the%20road%20blocks%20in%20the%20way%20of%20learning%20are%20mental.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20resounding%20advice%C2%A0is%20simple%3A%20Approach%20learning%20with%20a%20playful%2C%20fun%20state%20of%20mind%20(like%20a%20child)%2C%20make%20mistakes%2C%20and%20try%20to%20really%20live%20the%20language%20%E2%80%94%20listen%20to%20music%2C%20watch%20foreign%20movies%2C%20play%20video%20games.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJust%20like%20with%20anything%2C%20making%20a%20habit%20out%20of%20it%20certainly%20helps.%20If%20you%20can%20spend%20as%20little%20as%2030%20minutes%20a%20day%20(which%20we%20all%20have%20%E2%80%94%20on%20the%20subway%2C%20waiting%20on%20line%2C%20before%20bed)%20you%E2%80%99ll%20make%20great%20headway.%20Like%20Matthew%20Youlden%2C%20a%20polyglot%20and%20Babbel%20language%20ambassador%2C%20explained%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DYr_poW-KK1Q%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehis%20TED%20talk%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20almost%20no%20one%20who%20speaks%20English%20knows%20all%20of%20the%20words%20in%20the%20English%20Oxford%20Dictionary.%20Fit%20the%20language%20to%20your%20life%2C%20and%20make%20it%20relevant%20to%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPolyglot%20Benny%20Lewis%20said%20he%20never%20successfully%20learned%20a%20second%20language%2C%20even%20after%20six%20months%20in%20Spain%2C%20until%20he%20approached%20learning%20like%20a%20passionate%2C%20fun%20project.%20Most%20speakers%20agree%20on%20this.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20fact%20of%20the%20matter%20is%20that%20unless%20you%20experience%20some%C2%A0miracle%2C%20you%20could%20very%20easily%20live%20your%20whole%20life%20without%20ever%20learning%20another%20language%20unless%20you%20make%20the%20decision%20to.%20It%E2%80%99s%20not%20something%20you%E2%80%99re%20likely%20to%20learn%20just%20by%20switching%20your%20iPhone%E2%80%99s%20language%20to%20Spanish%20or%20labeling%20your%20kitchen%20appliances%20with%20translations%2C%20so%20you%20might%20need%20(and%20want)%20supplements%20like%20language%20apps%20or%20the%20well-trusted%20Rosetta%20Stone%20set.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20originally%20published%20on%C2%A08%2F8%2F2017.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBelow%20are%20eight%20ways%20to%20learn%20a%20new%20language%20that%20incorporate%20a%20fun%20mentality%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWatch%20a%20film%20with%20subtitles%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22980%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%2271Y3fo1zSXL._SX522_%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5989d6b04fc3c02d008b6886%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22784%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20way%20to%20make%20the%20language%20fun%2C%20naturally%20integrated%2C%20and%20let%20you%20%26quot%3Blive%20it%26quot%3B%20is%20by%20listening%20to%20it%20in%20a%20movie%20with%20or%20without%20subtitles%20of%20your%20native%20language.%20You'll%20get%20a%20feel%20for%20the%20sounds%2C%20patterns%2C%20and%20rhythms%20of%20the%20language%20as%20well%20as%20learn%20something%20about%20the%20culture%2C%20or%2C%20at%20the%20very%20least%2C%20a%20couple%20directors.%20It's%20a%20nice%20way%20to%20turn%20a%20relaxing%20activity%20into%20a%20broadening%20of%20horizons%20and%20vocabulary.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f931edb0-dd74-4439-98a4-8d8775469ca5%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Famzn.to%2F2hFp7dr%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAm%C3%A9lie%2C%20multi-format%2C%20%247.99%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EDownload%20a%20really%20fun%20app%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22980%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Screen%20Shot%202017%2008%2008%20at%2011.26.02%20AM%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5989d86d4fc3c0bb188b4d91%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22784%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EiTunes%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20a%20reason%20this%20was%20Apple's%20iPhone%20App%20of%20the%20Year.%20It%20makes%20language%20learning%20fun%2C%20and%20many%20features%20are%20free%20(even%20though%20there%20are%20in-app%20purchases).%20I%20personally%20use%20this%20app%20(it%20alone%20helped%20prepare%20me%20for%20a%20semester%20abroad)%2C%20and%20I%20love%20that%20I've%20found%20a%20productive%20and%20low-key%20way%20to%20pass%20spare%20time%20that%20I%20might%20otherwise%20do%20nothing%20useful%20with.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cd98e51a-f859-47d1-aa73-f114b9b9baa4%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fitunes.apple.com%2Fus%2Fapp%2Fduolingo-learn-spanish-french-and-more%2Fid570060128%3Fmt%3D8%26at%3D1001loVS%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDuolingo%2C%20free%20to%20download%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EPlay%20a%20game%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22980%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%2261p9QmTSjGL._SL1001_%