ducts%25252Fthe-body-lotion%25253Fvariant%25253D10872112349299%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Body%20Lotion%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20is%20Christiansen's%20favorite%20product%20in%20the%20line.%20It's%20nothing%20short%20of%20perfect.%20It%20sinks%20right%20in%20and%20keeps%20my%20dry%20elbows%20moisturized%20all%20day%20long%20%E2%80%94%20like%20a%20lightweight%20moisturizer%20that%20just%20happens%20to%20be%20used%20all%20over%20your%20skin.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20like%20a%20daily%20multi-vitamin%20for%20skin%20health%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%20%26quot%3BThere%20are%20several%20vitamins%20and%20nutrients%20coming%20from%20the%20three%20oils%20we're%20using%20in%20the%20formula%3A%20marula%2C%20cacay%2C%20and%20meadowfoam%20oil.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20inclusion%20of%20oils%2C%20the%20product%20absorbs%20almost%20instantly.%20You%20know%20how%20you%20usually%20have%20to%20wait%2015%20minutes%20between%20slathering%20on%20a%20typical%20body%20lotion%20and%20pulling%20on%20your%20skinny%20jeans%3F%20(Just%20me%3F)%20There's%20zero%20downtime%20with%20N%C3%A9cessaire.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20nofollow%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15126318701p3-20%26h%3Dfa953bafe6989af3694400b0b5659054369975b7658cec069c40efa6808ff64e%26postID%3D61b8efc7f2a36b1ac9f4234a%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fbeauty%252Fnecessaire-review%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fclick.linksynergy.com%252Fdeeplink%253Fid%253DEHFxW6yx8Uo%2526amp%253Bmid%253D44052%2526amp%253Bmurl%253Dhttps%25253A%25252F%25252Fnecessaire.com%25252Fproducts%25252Fthe-body-lotion%25253Fvariant%25253D10872112349299%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Body%20Lotion%3C%2Fa%3E%20also%20features%20a%20healthy%20dose%20of%20skin-strengthening%20peptides%2C%20which%20skincare%20enthusiasts%20will%20recognize%20as%20a%20facial-care%20ingredient.%20%26quot%3BPeptides%20are%20predominantly%20used%20in%20facial%20skincare%2C%26quot%3B%20Christiansen%20agrees%2C%20%26quot%3Bbut%20we%20felt%20it%20was%20worth%20it.%20They%20firm%20and%20tone%20skin%20over%20time.%26quot%3B%20And%20firm%2C%20toned%20skin%20is%20something%20everyone%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0male%2C%20female%2C%20and%20beyond%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0can%20appreciate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EA%20focus%20on%20safe%2C%20sustainable%20products%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EN%C3%A9cessaire's%20other%20admirable%20mission%20is%20making%20sure%20its%20products%20are%20100%25%20safe%20to%20use%20%E2%80%94%20which%2C%20I%20admit%2C%20%3Cem%3Eseems%3C%2Fem%3E%20like%20it%20should%20be%20a%20no-brainer%2C%20right%3F%20But%20since%20the%20personal-care%20industry%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fda.gov%2Fcosmetics%2Fproductsingredients%2Fingredients%2Fdefault.htm%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eisn't%20regulated%20by%20the%20US%20Food%20and%20Drug%20Administration%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20products%20are%20often%20made%20with%20probable%20or%20proven%20carcinogens%20(like%20phthalates%20and%20formaldehyde)%20and%20%26quot%3Bendocrine%20disruptors%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20are%20known%20to%20interfere%20with%20hormone%20production%20(like%20pesticides%20and%20the%20preservative%20BHA).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20speak%20a%20lot%20about%20being%20clean%2C%20which%20is%20a%20fancy%20word%20for%20non-toxic%20ingredients%20that%20we%20deliver%20with%20our%20No%20List%2C%26quot%3B%20Christiansen%20explains.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20nofollow%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15126318701p3-20%26h%3D494629dbdbd387b4510f8bde93feee3110e17d57e7f6f224322a1b8343ef20ea%26postID%3D61b8efc7f2a36b1ac9f4234a%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fbeauty%252Fnecessaire-review%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fclick.linksynergy.com%252Fdeeplink%253Fid%253DEHFxW6yx8Uo%2526amp%253Bmid%253D44052%2526amp%253Bu1%253Dbiip_040819_necessaire-body-care-review%2526amp%253Bmurl%253Dhttps%25253A%25252F%25252Fnecessaire.com%25252Fpages%25252Fthe-no-list%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20No%20List%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20essentially%20the%20brand's%20public%20call-out%20of%20potentially%20toxic%20ingredients%20it%20vows%20to%20never%20use%20in%20its%20products%2C%20including%20common%20offenders%20like%20parabens%2C%20sulfates%2C%20and%20silicones.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%20more%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fbeauty%2Fbest-face-moisturizer%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20best%20moisturizers%20you%20can%20buy%20to%20keep%20your%20skin%20happy%20and%20healthy%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221094%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Necessaire%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5cade20285c4b70cf4157843%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22821%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20products%20are%20housed%20in%20minimalist%20packaging%20that%20even%20my%20husband%2C%20who%20used%20to%20use%20the%20same%20bar%20of%20soap%20for%20his%20face%20and%20body%2C%20appreciates.%3Cp%3EN%C3%A9cessaire%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20say%20'no'%20to%20synthetic%20fragrance%20of%20any%20kind%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20adds.%20Besides%20typically%20being%20gender-specific%20(why%20do%20all%20women's%20body%20washes%20smell%20of%20flowers%20and%20candy%20while%20men's%20products%20boast%20scent%20names%20like%20%26quot%3BSteel%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BAnarchy%26quot%3B%3F)%2C%20fragrance%20can%20also%20irritate%20the%20skin.%20%26quot%3BWe%20offer%20a%20scent-free%20option%20for%20those%20of%20us%20with%20sensitive%20skin%20or%20for%20those%20who%20simply%20prefer%20to%20layer%20on%20their%20own%20scent%2C%26quot%3B%20Christiansen%20says.%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20a%20scent-free%20girl%2C%C2%A0so%20this%20option%20is%20personal%20to%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20we%20can't%20talk%20about%20a%20skincare%20product%20without%20talking%20about%20%23shelfie%20appeal.%20It%20was%2C%20after%20all%2C%20the%20packaging%20that%20convinced%20my%20husband%20to%20give%20the%20products%20a%20try%20in%20the%20first%20place.%20But%20what's%20even%20better%3F%20The%20packaging%20is%20sustainable%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20set%20out%20to%20reimagine%20personal%20care%20using%20clean%2C%20effective%20ingredients%20and%20with%20transparency%20and%20sustainability%20at%20our%20core%20%E2%80%94%20that%20is%20our%20mission%2C%26quot%3B%20Christiansen%20states.%20To%20this%20end%2C%20N%C3%A9cessaire's%20shipping%20materials%20include%20boxes%20made%20from%2085%25%20post-consumer%20waste%20and%20paper%20that's%20100%25%20recyclable.%20The%20company%20works%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fus.fsc.org%2Fen-us%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EForest%20Stewardship%20Council-certified%20vendors%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%20doesn't%20use%20virgin%20forest%20materials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20co-founders%20acknowledge%20that%20there's%20always%20room%20for%20improvement%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20environmental%20responsibility%2C%20which%20is%20why%20they%20foster%20open%20conversation%20with%20customers%20around%20the%20company's%20eco-friendly%20practices%20and%20keep%20the%20community%20updated%20with%20improvements.%20For%20example%2C%20Axelrod%20and%20Christiansen%20note%20that%20one%20of%20N%C3%A9cessaire's%20future%20goals%20is%20sourcing%20primary%20packaging%20that's%20100%25%20repurposed%3B%20in%20other%20words%2C%20no%20virgin%20plastic.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20consumer%2C%20I%20appreciate%20this%20transparency.%20It's%20something%20there's%20not%20enough%20of%20in%20the%20beauty%20industry.%20So%20many%20brands%20tend%20