20scenario.%20Both%20the%20shape%20of%20your%20hand%20and%20your%20primary%20use%20will%20change%20your%20definition%20of%20a%20great%20mouse.%20When%20choosing%20a%20computer%20mouse%2C%20consider%20the%20following%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOptical%20or%20Laser%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Optical%20and%20laser%20mice%20are%20quite%20similar%2C%20says%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.freegeek.org%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFree%20Geek%3C%2Fa%3E's%20Gilmore.%20Both%20use%20a%20camera-like%20sensor%20to%20look%20for%20changes%20in%20the%20surface%20to%20tell%20the%20computer%20how%20to%20move%20the%20cursor.%20A%20laser%20mouse%20uses%20a%20laser%20to%20light%20that%20sensor%20and%20tends%20to%20do%20a%20bit%20better%20on%20glossy%20surfaces.%20Some%20can%20even%20work%20on%20glass.%20But%20on%20a%20typical%20wood%20desk%2C%20most%20users%20won't%20notice%20a%20difference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDPI%20or%20CPI%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20dots-per-inch%20(or%20counts-per-inch)%20specification%20on%20a%20mouse%20is%20similar%20to%20the%20resolution%20of%20the%20sensor.%20A%20higher%20DPI%20means%20a%20faster%20mouse%2C%20Gilmore%20says%2C%20which%20is%20even%20more%20important%20when%20using%20a%20high-resolution%20monitor.%20A%20lower%20DPI%20mouse%20can%20be%20more%20precise.%20Some%20high-end%20mice%20allow%20you%20to%20choose%20different%20DPI%20settings%2C%20so%20you%20can%20switch%20based%20on%20whether%20you%20want%20speed%20or%20precision.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EConnectivity%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20A%20wireless%20mouse%20eliminates%20the%20cord%20but%20uses%20a%20USB%20dongle%20to%20connect%20to%20the%20computer.%20A%20Bluetooth%20mouse%20is%20similarly%20wireless%20but%20doesn't%20need%20that%20dongle%20to%20connect%20with%20a%20Bluetooth-compatible%20device.%20You%20might%20want%20to%20consider%20that%20option%20if%20you%20have%20limited%20ports.%20Take%20a%20look%20at%20wireless%20and%20Bluetooth%20mice's%20battery%20lives%20so%20you'll%20get%20a%20sense%20of%20how%20often%20you'll%20be%20charging%20them.%20Wired%20mice%20still%20have%20their%20place%2C%20particularly%20for%20gaming.%20Wireless%20and%20Bluetooth%20mice%20may%20introduce%20some%20lag%20that's%20noticeable%20in%20fast-paced%20games.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWeight%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ELighter%20mice%20are%20typically%20easier%20to%20move%20around.%20Fast-paced%20gamers%20tend%20to%20consider%20the%20weight%20of%20a%20mouse.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EComfort%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20How%20a%20computer%20mouse%20feels%20will%20depend%20on%20the%20size%20of%20your%20hand%2C%20says%20Kevin%20Weaver%2C%20a%20clinical%20assistant%20professor%20of%20physical%20therapy%20at%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsteinhardt.nyu.edu%2Fpeople%2Fkevin-weaver%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENew%20York%20University%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20is%20also%20certified%20by%20the%20Board%20of%20Certified%20Professional%20Ergonomists%20and%20the%20Oxford%20Institute.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20suggests%20using%20both%20hands%20with%20an%20ambidextrous%20mouse%20to%20halve%20the%20time%20spent%20on%20a%20mouse.%20%26quot%3BAs%20best%20as%20you%20can%2C%20centralize%20your%20mouse%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20look%20at%20most%20laptops%2C%20the%20touchpad%20is%20built%20into%20the%20base%2C%20right%20under%20the%20space%20key%2C%20in%20a%20centralized%20position.%20That's%20a%20best-case%20scenario%20because%20you%20can%20use%20your%20left%20or%20your%20right%20and%20have%20half%20the%20frequency.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20using%20your%20non-dominant%20hand%20feels%20too%20odd%2C%20he%20suggests%20choosing%20a%20contoured%20mouse%20that%20fits%20with%20your%20dominant%20hand.%20%26quot%3B%5BI%5Dt's%20important%20to%20go%20test%20these%20out%20in%20a%20showroom%20or%20store.%20One%20size%20does%20not%20fit%20all%2C%20one%20rule%20does%20not%20fit%20all%2C%26quo