20on%20an%20aluminum%20plate%20aesthetic%20are%20designed%20to%20let%20that%20customizable%20RGB%20light%20up%20like%20the%20Rockefeller%20Christmas%20tree.%20And%2C%20even%20though%20it%20is%20a%20full-sized%20keyboard%2C%20its%203.20cm-thin%20profile%20makes%20it%20feel%20less%20in%20your%20face.%20So%20much%20so%20you%20won't%20be%20embarrassed%20to%20use%20this%20at%20the%20office%2C%20especially%20because%20those%20keys%20are%20also%20elegantly%20quiet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20customizable%3A%20Razer%20Huntsman%20V2%20Analog%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Razer%20Huntsman%20V2%20Analog%20offers%20plenty%20of%20customizations%20that%20make%20it%20the%20best%20customizable%20gaming%20keyboard.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F60ede6fc61b8600019f16e18%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ERazer%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EType%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EFull%20optical%20keyboard%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ESwitch%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ERazer%20analog%20optical%20switch%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EInterface%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWired%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EFeatures%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EAdjustable%20actuation%2C%20Dual-step%20actuation%2C%20USB%203.0%20passthrough%2C%20magnetic%20leatherette%20wrist%20rest%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3C%2Faside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPros%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EAdjustable%20actuation%2C%20dual-step%20actuation%2C%20comfortable%20wrist%20rest%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECons%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EPricey%2C%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20learning%20curve%20with%20some%20features%2C%20heavy%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Razer%20Huntsman%20V2%20Analog%20isn't%20what%20most%20would%20call%20cheap%2C%20but%20it's%20also%20among%20the%20best%20value%20gaming%20keyboards%20out%20there%20thanks%20to%20its%20treasure%20trove%20of%20features.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe're%20not%20just%20referring%20to%20its%20unbelievably%20plush%20wrist%20rest%20that%20magnetically%20snaps%20onto%20the%20keyboard%20and%20makes%20your%20wrists%20feel%20like%20they're%20resting%20on%20clouds%20or%20the%20USB%20passthrough%20that%20offers%20another%20port%20to%20which%20you%20can%20connect%20other%20peripherals%20or%20the%20underglow%20RGB%20lighting%20that%20extends%20to%20the%20wrist%20rest.%20Although%20those%20do%20add%20to%20this%20keyboard's%20appeal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20importantly%20for%20gamers%2C%20the%20Razer%20Huntsman%20V2%20Analog%20is%20incredibly%20customizable%2C%20offering%20per-key%20adjustments%20and%20remapping%20like%20you've%20never%20seen%20on%20other%20keyboards.%20Via%20the%20Razer%20Synapse%20software%2C%20you%20can%20toggle%20each%20key's%20actuation%20point%20from%201.5mm%2C%20which%20is%20the%20default%2C%20to%203.6mm%2C%20so%20the%20keyboard%20responds%20to%20your%20presses%20exactly%20how%20you%20want%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat's%20nothing%2C%20however%2C%20next%20to%20the%20keyboard's%20dual-step%20actuation%20function%2C%20which%20actually%20lets%20you%20assign%20two%20different%20functions%20at%20two%20different%20actuation%20points%20on%20the%20same%20key.%20It's%20an%20incredibly%20nifty%20feature%20to%20have%2C%20as%20it%20gives%20you%20the%20ability%20to%20press%20fewer%20keys%20for%20similar%20game%20actions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20great%2C%20if%20basic%2C%20example%20of%20this%20would%20be%20to%20keep%20the%20W%20key's%20default%20%3Cem%3Eforward%3C%2Fem%3E%20action%20at%201.5mm%20actuation%20point%20while%20assigning%20the%20%3Cem%3Erun%20%3C%2Fem%3Eaction%20as%20its%20secondary%20function%20at%203.5mm%20in%20games%20like%20Valheim.%20It%20essentially%20eliminates%20the%20need%20for%20extra%20key%20presses%20and%20makes%20your%20gaming%20experience%20much%20more%20seamless%2C%20mimicking%20the%20dynamism%20of%20analog%20gamepads.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20essentials%20like%20customizable%20RGB%20lighting%2C%20macro%20recording%20%E2%80%93%20which%20can%20be%20done%20on-the-fly%2C%20onboard%20memory%20for%20up%20to%20five%20profiles%2C%20media%20keys%2C%20and%20robust%20doubleshot%20PBT%20keycaps%20are%20on%20hand%20as%20well.%20That's%20not%20to%20mention%20its%20super%20responsive%20and%20accurate%20performance%20thanks%20to%20its%201%2C000Hz%20polling%20rate%2C%20optical%20switches%20and%20N-key%20roll-over%20with%20anti-ghosting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20TKL%3A%20Roccat%20Vulcan%20TKL%20Pro%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22For%20smaller%20hands%20or%20smaller%20setups%2C%20compact%20but%20keep%20your%20arrow%20keys%20with%20the%20elegant%20Roccat%20Vulcan%20TKL%20Pro.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F60ede8cca8d8c00019b02f64%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ERoccat%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EType%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ETKL%20optical%20keyboard%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ESwitch%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ETitan%20optical%20switch%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EInterface%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWired%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EFeatures%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E1.4mm%20actuation%20distance%2C%20beautiful%20RGB%20lighting%2C%20volume%20dial%2C%20floating%20keys%20design%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3C%2Faside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPros%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ECompact%20form%20factor%2C%20quiet%20operation%2C%20short%20actuation%20distance%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECons%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EPricey%2C%20FN%20shortcuts%20take%20a%20bit%20of%20adjustment%2C%20bouncy%20feedback%20not%20for%20everyone%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20want%20the%20best%20tenkeyless%20(TKL%3B%20lacking%20a%20number%20pad)%20gaming%20keyboard%2C%20take%20a%20look%20at%20the%20Roccat%20Vulcan%20TKL%20Pro%2C%20which%20is%20among%20our%20favorite%20gaming%20keyboards%20at%20the%20moment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20optical%20option%20takes%20the%20classy%20route%20with%20its%20elegant%20and%20stunning%20aesthetic%20that%20features%20a%20floating%20keys%20approach%20on%20a%20brushed%20gunmetal%20finish.%20The%20whole%20thing%20seems%20to%20be%20designed%20to%20allow%20its%20customizable%20RGB%20lighting%20to%20shine%20brilliantly%2C%20which%20it%20does%20even%20in%20broad%20daylight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDon't%20let%20that%20elegant%20exterior%20fool%20you.%20The%20Roccat%20Vulcan%20TKL%20Pro%20is%20as%20robust%20as%20they%20come%2C%20boasting%20aircraft-grade%20aluminum%20and%20optical%20switches%20that%20are%20rated%20at%20100%20million%20keystrokes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20of%20those%20optical%20switches%2C%20they%20are%20Roccat's%20Titan%20optical%20switches%2C%20renowned%20for%20not%20just%20being%20durable%20but%20also%20for%20being%20extremely%20responsive.%20With%20an%20actuation%20distance%20of%201.4mm%2C%20you%20don't%20have%20to%20press%20those%20keys%20all%20the%20way%20for%20them%20to%20register%20%E2%80%94%20and%20accurately%2C%20we%20might%20add.%20In%20fact%2C%20we've%20typed%20up%20a%20song%20verse%20on%20this%20keyboard%20with%20very%20light%20presses%2C%20and%20it%20did%20not%20miss%20a%20single%20key.%20Combined%20with%20its%201%2C000Hz%20polling%20rate%2C%20you'll%20find%20this%20keyboard%20a%20huge%20advantage%20when%20gaming.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBecause%20it's%20incredibly%20quiet%2C%20you'll%20also%20have%20the%20peace%20of%20mind%20knowing%20that%20you%20can%20game%20late%20at%20night%20and%20not%20piss%20off%20your%20roommate%20with%20all%20the%20button-mashing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDon't%20worry%20about%20the%20more%20compact%20form%20factor%2C%20either.%20Its%20Function%20(FN)%20key%20shortcuts%20allow%20for%20quick%20access%20to%20media%20controls%2C%20settings%2C%20or%20RGB%20lighting%20presets%2C%20while%20the%20Roccat%20Swarm%20software%20lets%20you%20adjust%20keyboard%20settings%2C%20program%20key%20remaps%20and%20macros%2C%20and%20fine-tune%20the%20RGB%20lighting.%20There%20might%20just%20be%20an%20adjustment%20period%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20the%20price%20you%20pay%20for%20compactness.%20However%2C%20you%20definitely%20won't%20be%20missing%20out%20on%20full%20keyboard%20functionalities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20mini%3A%20Razer%20BlackWidow%20V3%20Mini%20Hyperspeed%20Phantom%20Edition%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Razer%20BlackWidow%20V3%20Mini%20Hyperspeed%20Phantom%20Edition%2C%20the%20best%20mini%20gaming%20keyboard%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F619e99fb1cffca0018862ef7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ERazer%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EType%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E65%25%20mechanical%20keyboard%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ESwitch%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Razer%20Green%20or%20Razer%20Yellow%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EInterface%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWireless%20and%20wired%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EFeatures%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThree%20types%20of%20connection%2C%20Phantom%20keycaps%2C%20Razer%20Hyperspeed%20Multi-Device%20support%2C%20Razer%20Chroma%20RGB%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3C%2Faside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPros%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EVery%20small%20form%20factor%2C%20fast%20performance%2C%20multiple%20connectivity%20options%2C%20robust%20build%2C%20floating%20keys%20appearance%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECons%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ENo%20dedicated%20arrow%20keys%2C%20steep%20learning%20curve%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fshop-links.co%2F1746123754822003079%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECorsair%20K65%20RGB%20Mini%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20our%20previous%20top%20choice%20for%20a%20mini%20keyboard%2C%20but%20it's%20been%20since%20toppled%20by%20the%20extremely%20versatile%20Razer%20BlackWidow%20V3%20Mini%20Hyperspeed%20Phantom%20Edition.%20The%20Corsair%20K65%20RGB%20Mini%20remainsan%20impressive%20piece%20of%20kit%2C%20especially%20to%20hardcore%20and%20pro%20gamers%20who%20need%20its%20ultrafast%20polling%20rate%20of%208%2C000Hz%20and%20onboard%20memory%20that%20stores%20up%20to%2050%20profiles.%20However%2C%20the%20Razer%20BlackWidow%20V3%20Mini%20Hyperspeed%20Phantom%20Edition%20is%20the%20mini%20keyboard%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20us%20who%20need%20versatility%20and%20comfort%20just%20as%20much%20as%20we%20do%20power.%20This%2060%25%20gaming%20keyboard%20boasts%20a%201%2C000Hz%20polling%20rate%20and%20on-board%20memory%20that%20lets%20you%20store%20up%20to%205%20profiles%2C%20which%20is%20more%20than%20enough%20for%20most%20non-pro%20gamers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20combines%20those%20capabilities%20with%20the%20versatility%20of%20having%20three%20different%20modes%20of%20connectivity%2C%20something%20that%20the%20fully-wired%20K65%20doesn't%20offer.%20What%20that%20means%20is%20that%20this%20mini%20gaming%20keyboard%20will%20let%20you%20connect%20it%20to%20your%20gaming%20PC%20or%20laptop%20via%20the%20Razer%20HyperSpeed%20Wireless%20(2.4%20Ghz)%20dongle%2C%20Bluetooth%2C%20or%20the%20detachable%20USB-C%20cable.%20And%2C%20all%20of%20them%20are%20almost%20equally%20reliable%20for%20gaming.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere's%20also%20a%20solid-keycap%20version%20of%20this%20keyboard%2C%20but%20we%20do%20adore%20the%20version%20with%C2%A0%20Phantom%20keycaps%2C%20which%20gives%20it%20the%20illusion%20of%20having%20low-profile%20floating%20keys%20and%2C%20in%20effect%2C%20letting%20that%20gorgeous%20RGB%20shine%20even%20brighter.%20For%20comfort%2C%20there's%20a%20tapered%20design%20that%20angles%20down%20towards%20your%20hands%20as%20well%20as%20an%20incredibly%20plush%2C%20mini%20ergonomic%20wrist%20rest.%20Though%20this%20wrist%20rest%20is%20sold%20separately%2C%20it's%20more%20than%20worth%20its%20%2420%20price%2C%20so%20much%20so%20this%20author%20uses%20it%20for%20all%20her%20keyboards%2C%20even%20the%20non-gaming%20ones.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERounding%20all%20that%20out%20are%20the%20keyboard's%20fully%20programmable%20keys%2C%20on-the-fly%20macro%20recording%20capabilities%2C%20and%20an%2080-million-keystroke%20lifespan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20wireless%3A%20Logitech%20G915%20Lightspeed%20Wireless%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Logitech%20G915%20TKL%20Tenkeyless%20Lightspeed%20Wireless%20RGB%E2%80%99s%20wireless%20performance%20makes%20the%20best%20wireless%20gaming%20keyboard.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F60edeb36a8d8c00019b02f7a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EType%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ETKL%20mechanical%20keyboard%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ESwitch%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ELow%20Profile%20GL%20tactile%20switch%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EInterface%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWireless%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EFeatures%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EDual%20device%20connectivity%2C%20onboard%20memory%2C%20low%20profile%20switches%2C%20fully%20customizable%20per-key%20lighting%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3C%2Faside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPros%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EGreat%20performance%2C%20incredibly%20thin%20profile%2C%20long%20battery%20life%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECons%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EExpensive%2C%20no%20numeric%20pad%2C%20not%20all%20keys%20are%20programmable%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Logitech%20G915%20TKL%20Tenkeyless%20Lightspeed%20Wireless%20RGB%20is%20one%20good%20looking%20keyboard%2C%20with%20its%20thin%20floating%20keycaps%2C%20brushed%20aluminum%20alloy%20top%2C%20round%20multimedia%20buttons%2C%20and%20beautiful%20RGB%20lighting.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20doesn't%20just%20go%20by%20looks%20alone%2C%20however.%20Despite%20being%20one%20of%20the%20thinnest%20gaming%20keyboards%20out%20there%2C%20it%20also%20feels%20robust%2C%20its%20aluminum%20alloy%20top%20case%20supported%20by%20a%20steel-reinforced%20base.%20Meanwhile%2C%20its%20GL%20switches%20feel%20like%20they%20can%20take%20their%20share%20of%20button%20mashing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20other%20things%20to%20love%20here.%20Though%20it%20may%20not%20have%20an%20expansive%20feature%20set%2C%20it%20does%20come%20with%20its%20share.%20Those%20dedicated%20media%20keys%2C%20all%20round%20in%20shape%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20volume%20dial%2C%20are%20definitely%20useful%20additions.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20dedicated%20wireless%2C%20Bluetooth%2C%20game%20mode%2C%20and%20RGB%20brightness%20buttons%20are%20a%20boon%20to%20multitaskers%20who%20either%20use%20two%20devices%20at%20once%20or%20want%20to%20go%20from%20being%20productive%20to%20gaming%20in%20seconds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBecause%2C%20honestly%2C%20you'll%20love%20using%20this%20keyboard%20for%20typing%20up%20documents%20and%20writing%20those%20work%20emails%20as%20much%20as%20you%20would%20gaming%20with%20it.%20Combining%20a%201%20millisecond%20response%20time%20and%201.5mm%20actuation%20distance%20with%20its%20satisfying%20tactile%20feedback%2C%20it's%20just%20as%20comfortable%20to%20use%20for%20work%20as%20it%20is%20responsive%20and%20accurate%20for%20gaming.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20being%20our%20top%20wireless%20contender%2C%20there%20are%20a%20few%20noteworthy%20things%20here.%20It%20has%20two%20connectivity%20options%20%E2%80%94%20one%20via%20its%20Lightspeed%20USB%20receiver%2C%20the%20other%20via%20Bluetooth.%20This%20is%20something%20we%20often%20see%20with%20Logitech's%20wireless%20keyboards%2C%20but%20it%20isn't%20something%20we%20often%20see%20with%20wireless%20gaming%20keyboards.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Logitech%20didn't%20specify%20its%20Lightspeed%20USB%20receiver's%20range%2C%20we've%20used%20this%20keyboard%20six%20to%20seven%20meters%20away%20from%20the%20laptop%20it's%20connected%20to%20in%20another%20room%20with%20the%20door%20closed%2C%20and%20it%20didn't%20miss%20a%20single%20keypress.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20for%20less%20than%20%2450%3A%20Corsair%20K55%20RGB%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Corsair%20K55%20RGB%20may%20be%20cheap%2C%20but%20its%20performance%20and%20features%20prove%20that%20it%20can%20hold%20its%20own%20against%20its%20more%20expensive%20rivals.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F60edebf2a8d8c00019b02f8a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ECorsair%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EType%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EMembrane%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ESwitch%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ERubber%20Dome%20switches%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EInterface%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWired%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EFeatures%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EProgrammable%20macro%20keys%2C%20detachable%20palm%20rest%2C%20dust%20and%20water%20resistance%2C%20anti-ghosting%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3C%2Faside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPros%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ECheap%2C%20RGB%20lighting%2C%20customizable%20keys%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECons%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EKeys%20aren't%20mechanical%2C%20not%20fully%20programmable%2C%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20third%20time%20Corsair%20has%20featured%20on%20this%20list%2C%20though%20for%20good%20reason.%20Not%20only%20does%20the%20company%20build%20excellent%20top-tier%20keyboards%2C%20it%20also%20builds%20great%20affordable%20keyboards%20for%20the%20gamer%20on%20a%20budget.%20The%20best%20of%20those%20is%20the%20Corsair%20K55%20RGB%2C%20which%20comes%20in%20at%20less%20than%20%2450.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Corsair%20K55%20RGB%2C%20as%20the%20name%20suggests%2C%20offers%20full%20RGB%20lighting%2C%20making%20it%20look%20much%20more%20expensive%20than%20it%20really%20is.%20It%20also%20boasts%20a%20total%20of%20six%20programmable%20buttons%2C%20which%20can%20be%20programmed%20through%20the%20same%20great%20software%20you'll%20get%20with%20the%20K95%20Platinum.%20It%20also%20has%20dedicated%20media%20controls%2C%20and%20well-built%20keys.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20why%20is%20the%20keyboard%20so%20cheap%3F%20Well%2C%20those%20keys%20may%20be%20well-built%2C%20but%20they're%20not%20mechanical%20keys%2C%20and%20as%20such%2C%20they%20may%20not%20be%20as%20satisfying%20to%20press%20or%20durable%20as%20other%20gaming%20keyboards.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20that%20doesn't%20make%20this%20a%20bad%20keyboard%2C%20it's%20just%20something%20to%20keep%20in%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EHow%20we%20test%20gaming%20keyboards%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20buying%20computer%20peripherals%2C%20gamers%20often%20need%20something%20a%20little%20higher%20quality%20than%20everyone%20else.%20After%20all%2C%20when%20you're%20gaming%2C%20every%20millisecond%20counts%2C%20and%20the%20feel%20of%20a%20keyboard%20and%20mouse%20can%20have%20a%20pretty%20major%20effect%20on%20a%20gamer's%20performance.%20Those%20are%20the%20things%20we%20test%20when%20deciding%20whether%20or%20not%20a%20particular%20gaming%20keyboard%20is%20a%20worthy%20addition%20to%20this%20list.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20terms%20of%20performance%2C%20we%20typically%20see%20what%20a%20gaming%20keyboard%20does%20in%20the%20face%20of%20the%20latest%20popular%20games%2C%20playing%20a%20good%20mix%20of%20game%20genres%20on%20it.%20For%20example%2C%20we%20tested%20our%20most%20current%20picks%20above%20on%20AAA%20games%2C%20like%20Cyberpunk%202077%20and%20Resident%20Evil%20Village%2C%20as%20well%20as%20lower-budget%20but%20equally%20popular%20titles%2C%20like%20Valheim%20and%20It%20Takes%20Two.%20Of%20course%2C%20since%20most%20people%20often%20just%20use%20the%20same%20keyboard%20for%20productivity%20as%20they%20do%20for%20gaming%2C%20we've%20done%20our%20fair%20share%20of%20typing%20up%20emails%20and%20articles%20on%20these%20picks%20as%20well%2C%20which%20also%20helped%20us%20gauge%20each%20one's%20comfort%20level%2C%20tactile%20feedback%2C%20and%20overall%20typing%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20also%20make%20sure%20to%20test%20the%20software%20every%20keyboard%20utilizes%20for%20customizations%2C%20especially%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20macros%2C%20remaps%2C%20and%20RGB%20lighting.%20After%20all%2C%20many%20gamers%20rely%20on%20those%20supporting%20apps%20to%20improve%20their%20gaming%20experience.%20Naturally%2C%20if%20a%20gaming%20keyboard%20is%20wireless%2C%20we%20test%20its%20range%20and%20amount%20of%20latency%20as%20well%2C%20typically%20by%20taking%20it%20as%20far%20as%20we%20can%20from%20the%20PC%20it's%20connected%20to%20or%20in%20another%20room%20and%20using%20it%20like%20we%20normally%20would.%20Finally%2C%20we%20test%20specific%20features%20as%20well%20%E2%80%94%20for%20example%2C%20if%20a%20keyboard%20has%20some%20specifically%20for%20MMORPG%20and%20MOBA%2C%20we%20make%20sure%20to%20utilize%20such%20features%20for%20such%20online%20multiplayer%20games.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWhat%20to%20look%20for%20in%20a%20gaming%20keyboard%3Cp%3EMore%20so%20than%20gaming%20PCs%20or%20laptops%2C%20the%20ideal%20gaming%20keyboard%20for%20one%20person%20isn't%20necessarily%20going%20to%20be%20the%20same%20for%20another.%20It%20highly%20depends%20on%20a%20number%20of%20factors%2C%20including%20gaming%20preferences%2C%20budget%2C%20space%2C%20and%20comfort.%20So%2C%20let's%20try%20to%20narrow%20yours%20down%20for%20you%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EType%20of%20switches%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20high-quality%20gaming%20keyboards%20opt%20for%20mechanical%20switches%2C%20of%20which%20there%20are%20also%20several%20subtypes%3A%20linear%2C%20tactile%2C%20and%20clicky.%20Do%20bear%20in%20mind%20that%20different%20manufacturers%20have%20their%20own%20names%20for%20these%20subtypes%20%E2%80%93%20Razer%2C%20for%20example%2C%20calls%20its%20own%20mechanical%20switches%20Green%20(tactile%20and%20clicky)%2C%20Yellow%20(linear%20and%20silent)%20and%20Orange%20(tactile%20and%20silent).%20This%20means%20that%20choosing%20the%20mechanical%20switch%20you%20like%20most%20is%20actually%20a%20bit%20more%20involved%2C%20and%20for%20that%2C%20you%20should%20check%20out%20our%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fmechanical-keyboard-switches%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThere%2520are%2520three%2520kinds%2520of%2CReference%2520library%2520for%2520more%2520stories.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGuide%20to%20Mechanical%20Switches%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20then%20there%20are%20keyboards%20that%20use%20optical%20switches%2C%20which%20tend%20to%20have%20faster%20actuation%20and%20longer%20lifespans%20in%20general.%20Of%20course%2C%20with%20these%20two%20types%20of%20switches%20competing%20against%20one%20another%2C%20this%20isn't%20necessarily%20a%20hard%20and%20fast%20rule.%20There%20are%20mechanical%20switches%20out%20there%20that%20now%20have%20just%20as%20long%20of%20a%20lifespan%20as%20optical%20ones%2C%20for%20example.%20And%2C%20while%20most%20people%20prefer%20the%20feel%20and%20feedback%20that%20mechanical%20switches%20offer%2C%20some%20optical%20switches%20have%20managed%20to%20deliver%20that%20same%20satisfying%20feel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20some%20gaming%20keyboards%20%E2%80%93%20usually%20the%20budget%20ones%20%E2%80%93%20come%20with%20membrane%20switches%2C%20which%20have%20very%20little%20tactile%20feedback%20but%20tend%20to%20be%20cheaper%20and%20can%20allow%20the%20keyboards%20to%20be%20waterproof.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESize%2C%20layout%20and%20form%20factor%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20full-sized%20gaming%20keyboards%20out%20there%2C%20which%20is%20likely%20the%20type%20of%20keyboard%20most%20gamers%20have.%20But%2C%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20manufacturers%20have%20come%20to%20realize%20the%20value%20of%20smaller%20ones.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETKL%2C%20or%20TenKeyLess%2C%20gaming%20keyboards%20were%20the%20first%20to%20really%20hit%20the%20mainstream%2C%20abandoning%20the%20number%20pad%20and%20other%20miscellaneous%20keys%20most%20people%20don't%20need%20for%20gaming%20use%20to%20save%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%20mini%20%E2%80%93%20or%2060%25%2C%2065%25%20and%2075%25%20%E2%80%93%20keyboards%20hit%20the%20shelves%2C%20offering%20that%20extremely%20compact%20and%20portable%20form%20factor%20to%20gamers%20with%20smaller%20spaces%20and%20setups.%20These%20are%20definitely%20ideal%20if%20you%20have%20a%20small%20or%20already%20overcrowded%20desk.%20However%2C%20these%20have%20really%20steep%20learning%20curves.%20You%20will%20be%20sacrificing%20small%20luxuries%20like%20having%20easy%20access%20to%20your%20arrow%20keys%2C%20which%20means%20you'll%20have%20to%20take%20time%20to%20program%20or%20learn%20shortcuts%20before%20diving%20into%20your%20games.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhichever%20size%2Flayout%20you%20choose%2C%20you'll%20find%20some%20thick%20ones%20and%20some%20with%20very%20thin%20profiles.%20These%20come%20with%20their%20own%20advantages%20and%20disadvantages%20as%20well%2C%20which%20means%20that%20the%20right%20one%20for%20you%20greatly%20depends%20on%20your%20comfort%20level%20and%2C%20to%20an%20extent%2C%20the%20size%20of%20your%20hands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EConnectivity%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20most%20gamers%2C%20a%20wired%20connection%20is%20still%20king%2C%20which%20is%20true%20in%20some%20ways.%20You%20don't%20have%20to%20worry%20about%20battery%20life%20or%20your%20connection%20getting%20cut%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20a%20pivotal%20game%20moment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20wireless%20gaming%20keyboards%20have%20come%20a%20long%20way%20in%20terms%20of%20performance%2C%20accuracy%2C%20and%20connectivity.%20Choose%20one%20of%20the%20best%20wireless%20options%20out%20there%2C%20and%20you're%20pretty%20much%20guaranteed%20the%20same%20quality%20as%20their%20wired%20counterparts.%20And%2C%20these%20tend%20to%20also%20have%20very%20long%20battery%20lives.%20The%20only%20thing%20is%20that%20you%20do%20have%20to%20remember%20to%20charge%20it%20once%20in%20a%20while.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPerformance%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20gaming%20keyboards%2C%20performance%20is%20key%2C%20no%20matter%20the%20type%20of%20games%20you%20typically%20play.%20However%2C%20there%20are%20also%20different%20levels%20of%20performance%20ideal%20for%20different%20types%20of%20games.%20An%208%2C000Hz%20polling%20rate%20might%20be%20the%20dream%2C%20for%20example%2C%20but%20realistically%2C%20a%201%2C000Hz%20one%20should%20be%20more%20than%20enough%20for%20gamers%20not%20playing%20at%20pro%20levels.%20And%2C%20keyboards%20with%201%2C000Hz%20polling%20rates%20tend%20to%20be%20cheaper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMake%20sure%20to%20get%20something%20with%20N-key%20rollover%20and%20anti-ghosting%20features%20if%20the%20games%20you%20play%20tend%20to%20require%20a%20lot%20of%20button-mashing%2C%20fast%20presses%2C%20or%20macros%2C%20as%20these%20ensure%20that%20the%20keyboard%20registers%20every%20single%20key%20your%20press%2C%20no%20matter%20how%20fast%20in%20succession%20you%20do%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFeatures%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20basic%20keyboards%20tend%20to%20be%20minimal%20in%20features%2C%20but%20pricier%20ones%20come%20kitted%20out%20with%20things%20like%20onboard%20memory%20to%20store%20profiles%20and%20macros%20in%2C%20dedicated%20media%20controls%2C%20fully%20programmable%20keys%2C%20and%20an%20included%20wrist%20rest.%20Before%20you%20hit%20buy%2C%20make%20sure%20you%20know%20which%20features%20are%20vital%20to%20you%20so%20you%20can%20choose%20the%20gaming%20keyboard%20that%20offers%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWhat%20else%20we%20conside