nsider.com%2Fguides%2Fbeauty%2Fbest-conditioner%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econditioner%3C%2Fa%3E%20just%20put%20in%20during%20your%20shower.%20The%20Volo%20towel%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20absorbs%20water%20and%20dries%20my%20hair%20efficiently%20without%20damaging%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%20more%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fbeauty%2Fturbie-twist-hair-towel-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThis%20%2410%20hair%20towel%20is%20deceptively%20simple%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20literally%20just%20a%20towel%20with%20some%20small%20design%20tweaks%2C%20but%20I%20swear%20by%20it%20for%20drying%20my%20hair%20quickly%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22volo%20hair%20towel%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5d65465d2e22af0f7c0cbcb2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EVolo%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EThe%20bottom%20line%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20this%20means%20I%20spend%20less%20time%20drying%20my%20hair%20and%20my%20hair%20is%20less%20damaged.%20The%20payoff%20of%20making%20it%20to%20bed%20or%20to%20an%20event%20with%20smooth%2C%20dry%20hair%20every%20time%20is%20well%20worth%20the%20%2439%20upfront%20cost.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fbeauty%2Fvolo-hero-hair-towel-review%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1776977925000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5d65390d2e22af118b449d7c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fbeauty%2Fvolo-hero-hair-towel-review%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Volo%20Hero%20is%20a%20large%20towel%20said%20to%20absorb%2010%20times%20its%20weight%20in%20water.%20I%20tried%20