s-2-1757073511-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fpunjab-floods-2-1757073511-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fpunjab-floods-2-1757073511-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fpunjab-floods-2-1757073511-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-496945%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EKalgidhar%20Trust%20is%20one%20of%20the%20many%20NGOs%20conducting%20relief%20and%20rescue%20operations%20on%20the%20ground%2C%20supported%20by%20Donatekart%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20important%20to%20note%20that%20while%20the%20NGO%20partners%20on%20the%20ground%20will%20be%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F287345%2Fseeds-disaster-cyclone-earthquake-india-how-to-build-safe-homes-schools%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edistributing%20the%20relief%20kits%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20funds%20will%20be%20directly%20channelled%20towards%20procuring%20the%20necessary%20material%20and%20will%20not%20be%20directed%20to%20NGOs%20themselves.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYour%20money%20is%20directly%20helping%20a%20flood%20victim.%20Your%20donations%20will%20go%20towards%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E1)%20airlifting%20the%20boats%20to%20the%20sites%20of%20rescue%20operations%20and%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2)%20procuring%20relief%20material%20so%20that%20families%20can%20be%20helped%20once%20they%20are%20shifted%20to%20the%20relief%20centres.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.donatekart.com%2FDisaster-Relief%2FThe-Better-India%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Clabel%3EDONATE%20NOW%20%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fa%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%